Bî Jesu Krristi<TS3>(<a href="b42.2.1-7">Luk 2:1-7</a>)Me̱di bî Jesu Krristi e̱ i shi he ni: De̱ ngu Merri e̱ i sa ꞌjee ngu shi rwe nyrra ne Usufu; me̱di we ne mbe rishi yaa ko, á timi ne ngu bi ehwie a yarri igbe̱ Nshe Wiri.<RF q=+><a href="b42.1.27">Luk 1:27</a>
Aha ncwa ngu Usufu a nyi nze̱we ne ngu bi redziee, ko ce̱ he ngu ki ci nshwu we̱, ngu a hwie he ngu ki we ranranng.
Me̱di a zhe ne ngu shi hwie nka ni, ya njeli Brrabe̱ ya wre̱ nwie ngu a revi ngu a he ne ngu he, “Usufu, ewe Dooda, shi de̱ ngwe̱ ci owu ne fo Merri re hwie̱ mbrru ngwe̱ we̱, aha ewe ne ngu shi hwie ngu a wru nwie Nshe Wiri.
A shi bî nze̱we, ngbe ngwe̱ ki ci lo he Jesu<RF q=+>Jesu:Lo “Jesu” a shi a zhe nka Heleni, a zhe nka nné Ibrrani a nyi “Joshwua.” Maana nna nyi nke he, “Brrabe̱ kyiá nneywí.”, aha a ri kyia nné ngu ne re-e̱ngwie̱ mbe.”<RF q=+><a href="b42.1.31">Luk 1:31</a>
Re-ankya ne̱ á ci zhwozhwo ni aha ngbe kya ne Brrabe̱ i he re ci rrurru shi ne nne ti re̱se̱ng ngu i he,
“Ri, ewena nna ri se̱ ehwie,we̱ bî ewerento,á ri ki ye he Imanuwe.”Maana nna nyi nke he, “Be̱ne̱ shi ngbe nzhi.”<RF q=+><a href="b23.7.14 (LXX)">Ish 7:14 (LXX)</a>
A zhe ne Usufu ngu shwo ndzie, ngu a nyi shi kya ne njeli Brrabe̱ ki heng he re nyi. Aa fo Merri hwie̱ mbrru ngu.
Me̱di koo ree nywe̱ ngbe ne ngu we̱ he̱rri aa ma bî ewe. Ngu a ki ci lo he Jesu.
Nné hu re̱nde̱ be dzie JesuA zhe ne e bî Jesu a Be̱talahami a ngwie̱ Yahudi, a i nyi Hirridu ngu nyi nggwe̱. Yá nné hu re̱nde̱ e̱ wru gbong a nva ze á be Urrushelima.
Á rin he, “Nggwe̱ nné Yahudi ne e bî e̱ shi he? Nzhi ri e̱nde̱ ngu a nva ze,<RF q=+>Nzhi ri e̱nde̱ ngu a nva ze:KaNzhi ri e̱nde̱ ngu a zhe ne ngu shi wru. nyi ngwiee nzhi be ngbe nzhi ki ye mbe.”
A zhe ne Nggwe̱ Hirridu ho ni, ngu a ne̱ ne bē ngbe ga nné Urrushelima zhwozhwo.
Aa ye nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nné mie̱ nneywí Nti Nka Musa zhwozhwo nwie we rinng he, “Ewie ne e shi ning bî Krristi<RF q=+>Krristi:Ka ré he “Masiha.” nna nyi he?”
Á ki shing he, “A Be̱talahami a ngwie̱ Yahudi, aha nne ti re̱se̱ng i wie ye̱ye̱rri ni he,
Wire Hirridu a ye nné hu re̱nde̱ nna a la la aha ngbe ngu hu ye̱ye̱rri zhe ne e̱nde̱ nna ngu i ning wru.
A zhe ne ngu shi we cire re nzhi Be̱talahami ngu a he ne mbe he, “Nyi ywa, nyi ya kre ewe nna we sheng. We ne nyi ri ki she, nyi ning ting, aha ngbe n ya ki ye mbè ma.”
A zhe ne mbe ho nka nggwe̱, mbe e̱ ne̱ ne ciee mbe, ngbe e̱nde̱ ne mbe ri ri a nva ze e̱ ngu a we kwa yincwuee, aa ma ya yo a nwie ne ewe nna ngu ning shi.
A zhe ne mbe ri e̱nde̱ nna, rehwie mbe kla, á nyi rekwi we yang.
A zhe ne mbe ngwie a zonggru nna, á ya she ewe nna ngbe de̱ ngu Merri, mbe e̱ hu be mbe e̱ ki ye mbè. Wire mbe e̱ kla re-lente mbe, mbe e̱ trru re-ankya mbe e̱ ki na, a ning bi zinarriya ngbe turraren libanu ngbe na murru.<RF q=+>Zinarriya ... murru:Re-ankya ne̱ á nyi ngbá re-ankya bi ncwé̱ we yang ne ngwa nggwé̱. Zinarriya nyi ya kprincwe̱ ngu si gelgelgel; libanu nyi ya ntsi turraren bi ncwé̱ ne ngu bi shwe̱ rina ne nyi ne rishi ya ekwe; murru a ma nyi ya turraren ne nyi ne rishi ekwe ma, a nyi rikye̱ ne ci a kwe nne wire ré nyie̱.
Wire á ning brru cwo yaka rê re nzhi ngwie̱ mbe, aha á we ting a yarri revi he shi de̱ ré ning brru re nzhi nwie Hirridu wa we̱.
Usufu ngbe Merri to re nzhi MasarrA zhe ne mbe ne̱, ya njeli Brrabe̱ ya wre̱ a nwie Usufu a revi. A he ne ngu he, “Deze ngwe̱ fo Kowe ne̱ ngbe de̱ ngu a nyi to re nzhi Masarr. Nyi srra miimi se zhe ne nje ri he nka ne ngwe̱, aha Hirridu shi ci rekre ewe nna he ré ki yhwe̱.”
Aha nii, ngu a deze ngu a fo ewe nna ngbe ne de̱ ngu a totu mbe e̱ ne̱ re nzhi Masarr.
Á srra miimi he̱rri zheng hu Hirridu. Aha ngbe nka ne Brrabe̱ i he ne nne ti re̱se̱ng re ci rrurru shi ne e wie he, “Nje ye Kowe nje re wru a Masarr.”<RF q=+><a href="b28.11.1">Hos 11:1</a>
A zhe ne Hirridu ngu ya timi he nné hu re̱nde̱ ana á ki brra ne zentsi á ne̱, aa ci ehwie dzio we yang, ngu a ngwa nka he ré yhwi ga e̱we̱e̱ rewerento ne mbe bi rie wehwie re be be zhwozhwo a Be̱talahami ngbe re-nklang, ye̱ye̱rri ne zhe ne nné hu re̱nde̱ nna mbe i ki ting he mbe ning di e̱nde̱ nna.
Wire nka Brrabe̱ ne nne ti re̱se̱ng ne e ki ye he Irimiya ngu i he e̱ ci rrurru, shi ne ngu i he,
“Á hó cwue a Rrama,a nyi nku ne e ti ngbe anaa riywe̱ we yang,Rrahila<RF q=+>Rrama ... Rrahila:Rrama nyi ya kla a Be̱talahami ne ngu shi dudu ne Urrushelima. A nyi ewieng ku anaa riywe̱ rewe Isrreela, aha nné mbe i cwo miimi a zhe ne rwinkó mbe i we ko shi nné gyiaa re nzhi yaka ngwie̱. A bra shi dudu ne ewie ne i ning nyie̱ Rrahila mbrru Yakubu, de̱ rewe Isrreela, a zhe ne ngu i hu ne nyi riywe̱ we yang. cwe nku aha rewe ngu,ko bi ré ki krru ehwie we̱,aha koó ning shi we̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b24.31.15">Iri 31:15</a>
