Ngu a ya srra a ngwie̱ ne e ki ye he Nazarra. Aha nii, nka Be̱ne̱ ne nné ti re̱se̱ng mbe i he e̱ ci rrurru, shi ne mbe i he, “Á ri ki ye he Nne Nazarra.”<RF q=+><a href="b41.1.24">Mar 1:24</a>; <a href="b42.2.39">Luk 2:39</a>; <a href="b43.1.45">Yoh 1:45</a>
