Kundu ya nne ri níng he nka, nyi e̱ he, ‘Brrabe̱ ce̱,’ ngbe we̱ níng we nyi ne̱ mi we hwiehwie.”
Nke e̱ ci ni aha ngbe nka ne nne ti re̱se̱ng ngu i he re ci rrurru, shi ne ngu i he:
“Ti nné ngwie̱ Siyona he,<RF q=+><a href="b38.9.9">Zak 9:9</a>‘Ri, nggwe̱ ngwe̱ ree be nwie ngwe̱!Ko ne rogyrru we̱, me̱di a zete nze̱e̱kyia shi a zete ewe nze̱e̱kyi.’ ”
Nné ki zhwe á ywa á ya nyi ye̱ye̱rri shi ne Jesu we heng.
Á be mi ne nze̱e̱kyi ngbe ne eweng, á ning ta re-ankya rwe̱ mbe a zeteng, ngbe Jesu a ning ngra.
Brra rigwe̱ nneywí á ta re-ankya ci mbe a rê, kpi mbe kprre nva rekwe bi rohun á ta rê.
A zhe ne Jesu ngu ngwie a Urrushelima, ngwie̱ nna zhwozhwo fo re̱zhe̱ nwie rin he, “Nke e̱ nyi nye̱ ne̱?”
Rigwe̱ nné nna á kara he, “Ngu ne̱ nyi Jesu, nne ti re̱se̱ng ne ngu wru a Nazarra a Galili.”
Jesu ngwie a yarri Brranyi<TS3>(<a href="b41.11.15-19">Mar 11:15-19</a>; <a href="b42.19.45-48">Luk 19:45-48</a>; <a href="b43.2.13-22">Yoh 2:13-22</a>)Jesu a ngwie a yarri agrraa Brranyi, ngu a yu ga nné ne mbe rie̱ re-ankya ngbe nné sing zhwozhwo. Aa ywrru re-tebrru nné ne mbe shi bra ncwé̱ ngbe re-benci nné rie̱ re-vie̱kye̱.
Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Á wie he: ‘Á ri ye zonggru nje he zonggrung ku Be̱ne̱,’ me̱di nyi ki ci aa hwie̱ brra uugoo nné nca.”<RF q=+><a href="b23.56.7">Ish 56:7</a>; <a href="b24.7.11">Iri 7:11</a>
Nnencwué̱ ngbe nnenkú á be nwie ngu a Brranyi, ngu a we kyia.
Me̱di a zhe ne nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nné mie̱ Nti Nka mbe ri re-ankyang hwie̱ nga onu ne ngu nyi, ngbe ne e̱we̱e̱ rewe ne mbe shi kyie̱ re̱zhe̱ a agrraa Brranyi ré he, “Hosanna ne Kowe Dooda,” rehwie mbe yhwi.
Mbe e̱ ki rinng he, “Ngwe̱ ho kya ne e̱we̱e̱ rewe ne̱ mbe he e̱e̱?”<RF q=+><a href="b19.8.2 (LXX)">Rve 8:2 (LXX)</a>Jesu we shing he, “Ee, ko nyi ree hwieng gung we̱ e̱e̱? Nka Be̱ne̱ he, ‘Nyi e̱we̱e̱ rewe ngbe rewe shwo ne ngwe̱ we mie̱ng ré re de.’ ”
Ngu a we we, ngu a wru ci a yarri ngwie̱ nna re nzhi a Betani, ngu a ya kywe miimi.
Jesu yhwire ekwe riyhwietsie<TS3>(<a href="b41.11.12-14">Mar 11:12-14</a>, <a href="b41.11.20-24">20-24</a>)A brra nyiencwe ne Jesu ngu ya ning brru ngu cwo re be a yarri ngwie̱ nna, nzhwo ki yhwe̱.
Ngu a ri ekwe riyhwietsie a rekyi rê, ngu a ne̱ re nzhi ka ngu ya she bi gbre, me̱di aa ya she nyi we rohun. Ngu a he ne ngu he, “Ko ngwe̱ bra shi cinga yhwu gbre wa we̱!” We zhe zunzrru ekwe nna hwe.
A zhe ne nné ki zhwe ngu mbe ri ni, mbe e̱ hwie̱ nye̱ we ronu nwie rinng he, “Á ce̱ rimi ne ekwe riyhwietsie ne̱ ngu wre̱ ne hwe ni e̱e̱?”
Jesu he ne mbe he, “Cence nje níng ting he kundu nyi bi sa rie we̱sa ne nyi jinji, ko nyi we kya ne nje nyi ne ekwe riyhwietsie ne̱ ne nyi e̱ hung nying we̱, me̱di nyi e̱ hung he ne rugu ne̱ he, ‘Nga, ngwe̱ ya kpe a brra nzhwo rishi,’ ngbe we̱ ci ni.<RF q=+><a href="b40.17.20">Mat 17:20</a>; <a href="b46.13.2">1Kor 13:2</a>
Kundu nyi bi sa rie, ko nda ne nyi rin a zhe ne nyi shi ku Be̱ne̱ nyi e̱ she.”
Á rin Jesu nka aha de̱me̱ ngu<TS3>(<a href="b41.11.27-33">Mar 11:27-33</a>; <a href="b42.20.1-8">Luk 20:1-8</a>)Jesu a ngwie a yarri agrraa Brranyi; a zhe ne ngu shi mie̱ nka, nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe brrá nné Yahudi e̱ be nwie ngu, mbe e̱ ki rinng he, “Ngwe̱ she de̱me̱ ne ngwe̱ ning nyi re-ankya ne̱ a he? Nyi nye̱ ngu re ngwa zhwe de̱me̱ ne̱?”
Jesu we brang he, “Nje shi níng rin ya nka zunzrru. Kundu nyi ri ning shing, ma n níng ting ka nyi zohu de̱me̱ ne nje ning nyi re-cwuo ne̱ ye̱.
De̱me̱ ne Yohana i ning nyi batisma i wru a he? A i wru zinye̱ ka nwie nneywí?”Mbe e̱ ne̱ ne yaa ti ronu ce we nci mbe, mbe e̱ he, “Kundu nzhi ri he he wru zinye̱, we̱ níng rinng he, ‘Ma nyi nda ngu ci ne ko nyi shî nka Yohana we̱ e̱ ye̱?’
Kundu nzhi ri bra he he wru nwie nneywí, nzhi bra to owu nneywí aha ko nye̱ fo Yohana a nu nne ti re̱se̱ng.”
Aha nii, mbe e̱ he ne Jesu he, “Ko nzhi hu ma we̱.” Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Ko shi n níng ting ka nyi de̱me̱ nye̱ ne nje ning nyí re-ankya ne̱ ma we̱.”
Nka zhwebe rewe wehwie“Ma nyi hwie rimi ne nka ne̱? A i bi ya nne ne ngu bi rewe wehwie. Aa ywa a nwie hong, ngu a he, ‘A ewe, ywa ngwe̱ ya nyi cwuo a nhwie̱n inebi a cwu ne̱.’
“Ngu a he, ‘Ko nje cwo nzhi we̱.’ Aa srra ngu a ya hwie nka te̱nte̱, ngu a ywa.
“Wire ꞌbe̱ nna a ywa a nwie ya ewe nna, ngu a ya ki heng we shi ne ngu he ne na ce̱ucwung. Ngu a shî he, ‘Nje cwo nzhi,’ me̱di koo ywa we̱.
“Nyi zohu a zetsi mbe ne̱ ngu nyi kya ne ꞌbe̱ mbe e̱ ce̱?”Mbe e̱ shî he, “Na ce̱ucwung.”Jesu a he ne mbe he, “Cence, nje níng ting he: nné si gondu ngbe ntsie̱wenté á shi ke̱she nyi ré ngwie a Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱.
Aha Yohana Nyi Batisma be ngbe ngu níng ti rê redziee, ko nyi se̱ nka ngu we̱; me̱di nné si gondu ngbe ntsie̱wenté á se̱. Ko ngbe ne nyi zrre̱ ni, ko nyi hwie nka te̱nte̱ ngbe nyi se̱ nka ngu we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b42.3.12">Luk 3:12</a>; <a href="b42.7.29-30">7:29-30</a>
Nka zhwebe re-lebrra<TS3>(<a href="b41.12.1-12">Mar 12:1-12</a>; <a href="b42.20.9-19">Luk 20:9-19</a>)“Ma nyi ho ya nka zhwebe wa: Ya be̱ri ne ngu bi rebe aa kye̱ inebi a nhwie̱n ngu, ngu a no garru ngu a ning grrang. Ngu a kwe̱ ruvong yhwi ngbre inebi nna a kprahwan, ngu a no eri dede nang cwo nhwie̱n nna. Wire ngu a ko re-lebrra ré srra re ki nyi cwuo a nhwie̱n inebi nna, ngu a nyi ciee.<RF q=+><a href="b23.5.1-2">Ish 5:1-2</a>
A zhe ne ngbre nna sa dudu ré ne̱ ne kping, ngu a te yá hwié ngu a nwie re-lebrra nna he ré ya ki kpi ngbre na ngu.
“Me̱di re-lebrra nna á prre ꞌhwié nna, á cwe ya, á yhwe̱ ya, á ta ya ne ngbatsie.
He̱rri ne cwu aa te yá ꞌhwié nna wa re ne̱ na ce̱ucwung, re-lebrra á we nyi we shi na ce̱ucwung nna wa.
A ngrangrang, aa te ewe ngu nwie mbe, a he, ‘Nje hu he á cwo a to riyii ewe nje ne̱.’
“Me̱di a zhe ne re-lebrra nna mbe ri ewe nna, mbe e̱ ne̱ ne he we nci mbe he, ‘Yowe̱e̱! Ri nne ye gado nna nke. Nyi ning be nzhi ki yhwe̱ ngbe gado nna re hwie̱ ngge nzhi.’
“Ma kundu nne bi nhwie̱n ana ngu be, nyi hwie we̱ ya nyi rimi ne re-lebrra ana?”
Mbe e̱ he, “We̱ ci nné hwie̱ ana ré ci shweni, we̱ ngwa yaká re-lebrra nhwie̱n nna, ne mbe ri ma ki cwo mi ne ga na ngu, a zhe ne ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri ne e shi kpi ngbre nna.”
Jesu a he ne mbe he, “Ko nyi sa hwie a yarri krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ we̱ e̱e̱? Á wie he,‘Ngbaatsie ne nné runo mbe zhwu;aa bra ya hwie̱ te̱nte̱ ngbaatsie.Nyi Brrabe̱ ngu ki nyi ni;aa bra hwie̱ kyang nga onu a nwie nzhi.’<RF q=+><a href="b19.118.22-23">Rve 118:22-23</a>
“Aha nii, nje níng ting he, á shi níng trru ci a yarri Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱, ré ngwa nné mbiye ne mbe to owu Be̱ne̱ shi shi nné ne mbe shi be mi ne ngbre inebi ye̱ye̱rri.
[Nne ne ngu grre̱ a ngbaatsie ne̱, we̱ yaa kprre, me̱di nne nke ne ngbaatsie ne̱ kpe a zete ngu, we̱ ki mle̱ she̱she̱.”]
A zhe ne nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nné Farisi mbe ho re-nka zhwebe Jesu, á hu he a he re-nka ne̱ a rici mbe.
Mbe e̱ ne̱ ne kre rê mbe ki pie, me̱di á to owu rigwe̱ nné aha nneywí e̱ fo Jesu a nu nne ti re̱se̱ng.
Nka zhwebe bikyi nyrra<TS3>(<a href="b42.14.15-24">Luk 14:15-24</a>)Jesu we he ya nka zhwebe wa he:
“Ringgwe̱ zinye̱ shi shi ya nggwe̱ ne ngu nyi ewe ngu bikyi nyrra.
Ngu a te ꞌhwié ngu he ré ya ye nné, ne ngu we ti nyrra, ngbe re be a nwie bikyi nna, me̱di á ra be.
Ngu a te yaká ꞌhwié ngu, ngu a he ne mbe he, ‘Nyi ya ti nné ne nje we ti bikyi ne̱ he nje nyi ko nda yhwe̱. Nje ca ngbá re-izhimi ngbe dé̱ nnywá, nje nyi re-yâ nna yhwe̱ zhwozhwo. Nyi be bikyi nyrra nna fa.’
“Me̱di koó ci nkwile̱ gung we̱. Ko nye̱ mbe ne̱ ne ciee ngu, yá ne̱ re nzhi re-eyi mbe, yá ne̱ re nzhi nyi re-kaawe̱ mbe,
yá mbe prre ꞌhwié nna á we cwe he̱rri á we yhwi.
Ehwie nggwe̱ nna ye gbushwo. Ngu a ci re-shezhi ngu á ywa á ya we yhwi á shwi ngwie̱ mbe.
“Wire ngu a he ne ꞌhwié ngu he, ‘Nje nyi ko nda na bikyi nyrra ne̱ yhwe̱ wiriri, me̱di nné ne nje i we ti nyrra ne̱ koó mwa ye̱ye̱rri re be we̱;
nyi ywa a re-gasire, ko nye̱ ne nyi ri ki she nyi ki ye.’
Aha nii, ꞌhwié ngu á wru ci re nzhi brrá re-rê á ya tsu nné ne mbe she, re-te̱nte̱ng ngbe re-dedeng gbengbe mbe, á ya shi brra zonggrung nyi bikyi nna.
“Me̱di a zhe ne nggwe̱ nna ngu ngwie, ngbe ngu ri nné ice nna, ngu a timi ne ya nne a miimi ne ko ngu ci ankya bikyi nyrra we̱.
Ngu a ki rinng he, ‘A nu, ngwe̱ ce̱ rimi ne ngwe̱ ngwie he ne̱ we̱sa ci ankya bikyi nyrra a?’ Ko nne nna bi kya he we̱.
Nggwe̱ nna a he ne nnencwuó ngu he, ‘Nyi ki rrwe nva ngbe nta zhwozhwo, nyi ki zhwu ci a nwie ne ngu shi ywing, ne e níng kyie̱ rana re ye nnyi.’<RF q=+><a href="b40.8.12">Mat 8:12</a>; <a href="b40.25.30">25:30</a>; <a href="b42.13.28">Luk 13:28</a>
“Aha a nyi nné piriri ne e we ye, me̱di nyi nné tsie̱nzhwu ne e kyie.”
Trra Brra Nggwe̱ Rroma gondu<TS3>(<a href="b41.12.13-17">Mar 12:13-17</a>; <a href="b42.20.20-26">Luk 20:20-26</a>)Nné Farisi e̱ wru ci, á ya ne̱ ne rwe re-nka aha mbe hu rê ne mbe shi ning pie Jesu a re-nka nu ngu.
Mbe e̱ te nné ne mbe we zhwe ngbe nné ce̱ ringgwe̱ Hirridu he ré ya he ne ngu he, “Nne Mie̱ Nka, nzhi hu he ngwe̱ he we nka raywrra. Ngwe̱ mie̱ nneywí rê Be̱ne̱ ye̱ye̱rri. Ko ngwe̱ to riyii nneywí we̱, aha ko ngwe̱ ci nkwile̱ ne grime̱ nneywi we̱ ka re bra nyi nye̱.
Ma níng ting, a ri ngwe̱, aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri ré trra Brra Nggwe̱ Rroma gondu aa? Nzhi trra ka de̱ nzhi trra we̱?”
Me̱di Jesu hu he nyi we nka igerri, ngu a he, “Nyi nné brra ronu, nyi nda ngu ci ne nyi ce̱ ning mwa ri e̱ ye̱?
Nyi be mi ne ya cwe ncwe̱ng trra gondu a n ri!”Mbe e̱ ki be mi ne cwe denarri.
Ngu a we rinng he, “Nke e̱ nyi foto nye̱ ngbe lo nye̱ ne e ning wieng ne̱?”
Mbe e̱ he, “A nyi Brra Nggwe̱ Rroma.”Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Nyi ngwa Brra Nggwe̱ Rroma kya ne ngu nyi na ngu; nyi ngwa Be̱ne̱ kya ne ngu nyi na Be̱ne̱.”
A zhe ne mbe ho ni, á ne̱ ne nye̱ we ronu. Mbe e̱ ne̱ ki we fa.
Á he, “Nne Mie̱ Nka, Musa he ne nzhi he kundu ya nne hu we̱sa ne e̱we̱e̱ rewe, se gimbe ngu re fo kpambrru ngu re hwie̱ mbrru ngu, aha re ki bî rewe.
A i bi yá re-gimbe komo natsie̱ ne mbe srra ngbe nzhi. Na ce̱ucwung fo mbrru, aa ma ya hu we̱sa she e̱we̱e̱ rewe, ngu a we gimbe ngu ne mbrru nna.
Nne na ꞌhwie nyi we ni ma, he̱rri ngbe na ꞌtsie̱, he̱rri kpi mbe natsie̱ e̱ zhwozhwo á ning zhweng.
A ngrangrang, mbrru nna ma ya hu.
Ma a zhe ne ne̱, a tung deze nhu a, a ri nyi mbrru nye̱ a tsi mbe nné natsie̱ ana, aha ko nye̱ mbe nyi nyrra ne ngu?”
Jesu we shing he, “Nyi brru aha riywe̱ hu krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ ngbe igbe̱ ngu.
A zhe ne nneywí ri deze nhu, ko ntó ri ko mbrrú ka mbrrú ré drro re nzhi nyrra we̱. Nneywí ri shi shi re-njeli zinye̱.
A nkang deze nhu a, ko nyi hwie kya ne Be̱ne̱ ngu i he ne nyi e̱ we̱ e̱e̱? A he,
‘Nje nyi Be̱ne̱ na Ibrrahin, ngbe Be̱ne̱ na Ishaku, ngbe Be̱ne̱ na Yakubu.’ Ko nyi Be̱ne̱ nné kwi we̱, me̱di a nyi Be̱ne̱ nné nce.”<RF q=+><a href="b2.3.6">Wru 3:6</a>
A zhe ne rigwe̱ nné nna mbe ho ni, mbe e̱ ne̱ ne nye̱ we ronu ne mie̱ nka ngu.
Riti nka Be̱ne̱ na ngu ne̱ zhwozhwo<TS3>(<a href="b41.12.28-34">Mar 12:28-34</a>; <a href="b42.10.25-28">Luk 10:25-28</a>)A zhe ne nné Farisi mbe ho he Jesu drre̱ nné Sadukyi ne nka, mbe e̱ ya tsu.
