A he, “Nne Mie̱ Nka, nyi zohu ngu nyi brrang a tsi Nti Nka Be̱ne̱ e̱e̱?”
Jesu ki shing he, “ ‘Ce̱ Be̱ne̱ Brrabe̱ ngwe̱ ne onu rie ngwe̱ zhwozhwo, ngbe ce ngwe̱ zhwozhwo, ngbe ehwie ngwe̱ zhwozhwo.’<RF q=+><a href="b5.6.5">NNMN 6:5</a>
Nyi ngu ne̱ ngu nyi brrang ngbe cwucwung a tsi Nti Nka Be̱ne̱.
Na ꞌhwie a srra shi we ni wa: ‘Ce̱ nne dudu ne ngwe̱ shi rici ngwe̱.’
Ga Nti Nkang Mie̱ Nka Musa ngbe na nné ti re̱se̱ng á ria a Nti Nka wehwie ne̱.”
