Re-shezhi mi Jesu<TS3>(<a href="b41.15.16-20">Mar 15:16-20</a>; <a href="b43.19.2-3">Yoh 19:2-3</a>)Wire re-shezhi goona fo Jesu re nzhi a brra eri goona<RF q=+>brra eri goona:A nka Heleni á wie“prretorriya.”Prretorriya nyi riti nka Lati ne maana nna nyi brra eri ne goona nné Rroma ning srra. Kabeya a nyi eri ne Bilatu ning srra ko zohu zhe ne ngu be a Urrushelima, ka eri ne Hirridu ning srra. Re-shezhi Rroma piriri srra a eri nna.; mbe e̱ ye kpi brra rotsu re-shezhi zhwozhwo, á ya ki grra.
