Jesu kyia ya nne bi rije<TS3>(<a href="b42.4.31-37">Luk 4:31-37</a>)Jesu a ne̱ ngbe mbe re nzhi Kafanahu. Kotung Srra Cwu we she miimi, Jesu a ngwie zonggrung mwe, ngu a ne̱ ne we mie̱ nka.
