Ko bra bi nne ngu kro hwihwi rishi ruto a yarri gure kpe na rening we̱, aha kundu ngu nyi ni, rishi ruto nna we̱ ho gure kpe nna. Wire rishi ruto ngbe gure kpe nna wé̱ ci shweni gbengbe mbe. Se ka re kro hwihwi rishi ruto a yarri hwihwi gure kpe.”
Brrabe̱ na Kotung Srra Cwu<TS3>(<a href="b40.12.1-8">Mat 12:1-8</a>; <a href="b42.6.1-5">Luk 6:1-5</a>)Jesu i shi ciee a ya Kotung Srra Cwu nné Yahudi, ngbe nné ki zhwe ngu, ne mbe shi wara a yarri rebe yâ a yi. A zhe ne mbe shi ciee, nné ki zhwe ngu mbe e̱ ne̱ ne kpi yá re-nci alikama.<RF q=+><a href="b5.23.25">NNMN 23:25</a>
