A i ngwie a zonggru Be̱ne̱ a zhe ne Abiata ngu nyi Brra Prristi, aa ye yâ na ne e ngwá Be̱ne̱, ne se we re-prristi re ye, he̱rri aa ngwa nné ne mbe shi ngbe ngu.”<RF q=+><a href="b3.24.9">Liv 24:9</a>
