Jesu kyia nne bi re-rije<TS3>(<a href="b40.8.28-34">Mat 8:28-34</a>; <a href="b42.8.26-39">Luk 8:26-39</a>)Jesu ngbe nné ki zhwe ngu á tsa nzhwo rishi Galili re be a nyie Garasi.
