Ko nyi kya ne nneywi ngu ye ne ngu ki cí re bi le̱le̱ a nyyi Be̱ne̱ we̱. Me̱di nyi kya ne ngu wru yarri hwie ngu, ne ngu ki ci re bi le̱le̱ a nyyi Be̱ne̱.”
[Ko nye̱ ne ngu ri bi uucwung hong, nde re ho.]
A zhe ne ngu ne̱ nwie nneywí re si ri, nné ki zhwe ngu be ya ki rinng he re we ti cwu kya ne nka zhwebe ana ngu he.
Ngu a he ne mbe he, “He̱rri ne cwu nyi shi zhizhi e̱e̱? Ko nyi kya ne nneywi ngu ye, ne ngu ki cí re bi le̱le̱ a nyyi Be̱ne̱ we̱.
Aha ko kya ne ngu ye e̱ cwo a yarri onu rie ngu we̱, me̱di a cwo yarri hwie ngu, wire we̱ ya ki ti ci a uvu.” (Aha ni Jesu ti he ga re-nzhwe yâ zhwozhwo shi wiri a nyyi Be̱ne̱.)<RF q=+>Ko kya ne nneywi yé e̱ ci cinci a nyyi Be̱ne̱ we̱.
Ngu a wara ne we heng he, “A nyi kya ne ngu wrú a yarri hwie nka nneywi ne ngu ki ci re bi le̱le̱ a nyyi Be̱ne̱.
Aha a nyi a yarri yarri ronu rie nneywí ne re-hwie nka re-ankya e̱ngwie̱ mbe ning wrú shi: njè ngbe ya ewena ka ya nze̱we, ngbe nyi nca, ngbe yhwi nné,
ngbe nyi njè ngbe mbrru ya nne ka nto ya mbrru, ngbe ecwue mbrrú ngbe ntó, ngbe nyi ꞌhwie̱, ngbe ca rabrra, ngbe re-gre shweni, ngbe riyii ankya nné, ngbe kwe fe̱li, ngbe kywo rici ze, ngbe riywe̱ hwie nka te̱nte̱ng.
Ga re-ankya e̱ngwie̱ ne̱ á wrú a yarri hwie nka nneywi; nyi mbe ne mbe ci nneywi re bi le̱le̱ a nyyi Be̱ne̱.”
Sa rie ya mbrru<TS3>(<a href="b40.15.21-28">Mat 15:21-28</a>)Jesu deze miimi re nzhi a nva Taya ngbe Sido. Aa ngwie a ya eri. Ko zhwo ce̱ he nneywí ré hu he ngu shi miimi we̱. Gbengbe ni, nneywí ya ho.
We zhe ne ya mbrru ne e̱we̱ ewena ngu bi rije ya ho ni, ngu a wre̱ ne zhwu re be. Aa be ya hu be a nyyi ngu.
Ko mbrru nna nyi mbrru Yahudi we̱, á ki bî a nkla Finikyia a ngwie̱ Sirriya. A cwe nva ne Jesu he re ti rije ne ngu shi a yarri ewena ngu.
Me̱di Jesu he ne ngu he, “Nde e̱we̱e̱ rewe ré ke̱she ye ré shwe wire, aha koo mwa ye̱ye̱rri ngbe ré fo yâ e̱we̱e̱ rewe ré ngwa rovu we̱.”
Mbrru nna ki shing he, “Ee, a shi ni, Brrabe̱, gbengbe ni ma nje he ka rovu a á ta re-uucwu yâ ne mbe kpi be a gumong ye yâ e̱we̱e̱ rewe ne mbe ye ye̱ e̱e̱?”
Aha ni Jesu a he ne ngu he, “Aha zhwe nka ngwe̱ ne̱, ywa ne ciee ngwe̱, rije nna wru, aa we ewena ngwe̱.”
Aa ywa a ri ngu a ya she ewena ngu ne ngu shi nywe̱ be a zete gondo ne rije e̱ wru.
Jesu kyia ya rumwa<TS3>(<a href="b40.15.29-31">Mat 15:29-31</a>)Jesu we ngwie̱ Taya, aa cie̱ a Sido, ngu a ya cwo a Re-ngwie̱ Shwa, wire ngu a ya wro re be a Nzhwo Galili.
Jesu a wru mi ne nne nna nwie rigwe̱ nné re nzhi yaka ewie we nggaa ngu, ngu a gara nne nna nva a re-uucwu. Ngu a tsie rencwi, ngu a re le nne nna.
Ngu a gbi riyii zinye̱, ngu a fie̱ ncie̱ ne naana we yang, ngu a he ne ngu he, “Effata” (ne a zhe nka mbe e̱ he, “Kla!”)
We hwiehwie re-uucwu nne nna kla, le ngu wara ne ci ywaywa ngu a ne̱ ne he nka we cwancwancwa.
Jesu we gara nka he shi de̱ re ti ko ya nneng we̱. Me̱di a shi shi kundu ngu we gara nka ni wé̱ ke̱ we ne ning bra ti nka nna.
Nneywí ne̱ ne nye̱ we ronu we yang nwie he, “A nyi ko nda rina rina, he̱rri aa ci nné re̱n ré ho nka ngbe mwa ré he nka.”
Jesu ye ne nné ꞌci weni<TS3>(<a href="b40.15.32-39">Mat 15:32-39</a>)A rotu ana ya brra ekpri nné á ya tsu. Zhe ne mbe ya hwie̱ we̱sa ne kya ye, Jesu a ye nné ki zhwe ngu, ngu a he ne mbe he,
“Nje ri naana nné mbe rre e̱ ne mbe ci rotu wetsie̱ ngbe nje, mbe ya hwie̱ we̱sa ne kya ye ne̱.
Kundu nje he ne mbe he ré si ri ne nzhwo, wé̱ ya hwie̱ rê, aha yá mbe wru rewie ze̱nze̱.”
Nné ki zhwe ngu a he, “Ngwe̱ hwie he nyi he a eyi ne̱ ngbe ré ning she yâ ngbe re be ga nné ne̱?”
Jesu we rinng he, “Nyi cwú brredi wema nyi bi e̱?” Mbe e̱ kara he, “Natsie̱.”
Aa ci ga nné ana zhwozhwo ré srra be. Zhe ne ngu fo cwú brredi natsie̱ ana ngu a ning ci kijie̱ng, ngu a hwin ngu a kye nné ki zhwe ngu ngbe ré kye nnéng, mbe e̱ kye.
Á bi yá e̱wé̱ hwén tsie̱nzhwu, aa ning ci kijie̱ng wa, ngu a ngwa nné ki zhwe ngu ré kye wa.
Nneywí ye yâ á shwe he̱rri kya ne nné ki zhwe ngu mbe tsu ne ngu hwie̱ e̱ cwu grré natsie̱.
Nyi nné ntó ꞌci weni ne mbe i shi nwieng. Zhe ne ngu we cire,
ngu a ngwie a yarri konkro ngbe nné ki zhwe ngu re nzhi a nkla Dalmanuta.
Yá nné Farisi be nwie rin Jesu re-nka aha ne mbe ce̱ ki mwa mbe ri. Á he ne ngu he re we wru mi ne ya sheedeng hwie̱ nga onu a zinye̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.12.38">Mat 12:38</a>; <a href="b42.11.16">Luk 11:16</a>
Aa fie̱ ncie̱ ngu a he, “Nyi nda ngu ci ne nné nze̱ ne̱ mbe rin aha sheedeng hwie̱ nga onu aa? Nje níng ting cence, ko bi ko ya sheede ne e shi níng ngwa we̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b40.12.39">Mat 12:39</a>; <a href="b42.11.29">Luk 11:29</a>
Wire ngu a we we, ngu a ngwie a konkro, ngu a tsa nyie re nzhi yaka eme.
Yisi nné Farisi ngbe na HirriduGaa bru nné zhwe Jesu koó fo brredi we̱, se we zunzrru ne mbe bi a yarri konkro.
Jesu we gara nka he, “Nyi ci nkwile̱, nyi nyi te̱nte̱ ne yisi nné Farisi ngbe na Hirridu.<RF q=+>yisi:Yisi nyi kya ne e ci a ntsi felewang nyi brredi aha re hru. Me̱di a nka nné Yahudi e̱ a nyi nka zhwebe ne ngu tí he nne ne e ning he nka a brra onu.”<RF q=+><a href="b42.12.1">Luk 12:1</a>
Á ne̱ ne he re-nka we nci mbe he, “Kabeya, a he nka ne̱ aha ne ko nzhi bi brredi we̱ rre ye̱?”
Jesu hu kya ne mbe shi heng, ngu a we rinng he, “Nyi nda ngu ci ne nyi shi nwie he ko nyi bi brredi we̱ e̱e̱? He̱rri ne cwu ko nyi hu kya ne nje he ne̱ we̱ e̱e̱? Ko nyi pie cwu nka nna we̱ e̱e̱? A ke̱ we ne níng shi ywing a yarri rehwie nyi e̱e̱?
Nyi bi nyyi, me̱di ko nyi hung ring we̱ e̱e̱? Nyi bi re-uucwu, me̱di ko nyi ho we̱ e̱e̱? Ko nyi lu we̱ e̱e̱?<RF q=+><a href="b24.5.21">Iri 5:21</a>; <a href="b26.12.2">Ezi 12:2</a>; <a href="b41.4.12">Mar 4:12</a>
