Ngu a he, “A zhe ne nje i hwin cwú brredi natsie̱ ne nné ꞌci weni mbe i ye, nkla na mbe i hwie̱ ne nyi tsu a i ci grré wema?”Á shî he, “Natsie̱.”
A he ne mbe he, “He̱rri ne cwu ko nyi pie cwu nka nna fa we̱ e̱e̱?”
Jesu kyia nnencwue̱ a BesedaÁ ya wre̱ a nkla Beseda, yá nné e̱ be mi ne ya nnencwue̱, mbe e̱ cwe nva ne Jesu he re ki re ngbe re ki kyia.
Aa pie va nnencwue̱ nna, ngu a ki kwa he̱rri á wru nkla nna. Zhe ne ngu tsie rencwi a riyii nne nna, ngu a ki gara va, wire ngu a ki rinng he, “Ngwe̱ ri yankya aa?”
Aa gbi riyii ze ngu a he, “Nje ri nneywí, á shi shi nyi rekwe ne mbe cwo ciee re grra.”
Jesu he ne ngu he re se̱ we rê re si ri, ngu a ki gara nka he, “Shi de̱ ngwe̱ ning brru re nzhi nkla nyi we̱.”<RF q=+>Shi de̱ ngwe̱ ning brru re nzhi nkla nyi we̱:A yá re-tekpe krre̱de̱ ce̱ucwung na nka Heleni á wie he, “Shi de̱ ngwe̱ ning brru re nzhi nkla nyi ngwe̱ ya ne̱ ne ting we̱.”
