Mbe e̱ ki shing he, “Yá he he ngwe̱ nyi Yohana Nyi Batisma, yá a he ngwe̱ nyi Iliya, yá bra he ngwe̱ nyi ya a tsi nné ti re̱se̱ng.”<RF q=+><a href="b41.6.14-15">Mar 6:14-15</a>; <a href="b42.9.7-8">Luk 9:7-8</a>
Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Ma nyi e̱ rre, nyi he nje nyi nye ma?”<RF q=+><a href="b43.6.68-69">Yoh 6:68-69</a>Pita a he, “Nyi ngwe̱ ngwe̱ nyi Krristi.”<RF q=+>Krristi:A nka Ibrrani a nyi “Masiha,” nne ne e ki mia.
Jesu a we gara nka he shi de̱ ré ti ko ya nneng aha ngu we̱.
Jesu ti nka hu ngu<TS3>(<a href="b40.16.21-28">Mat 16:21-28</a>; <a href="b42.9.22-27">Luk 9:22-27</a>)Jesu ne̱ ne mie̱ nné ki zhwe ngu nka he se Kowe Nneywi re shwe ge̱zhe̱ we yang, he̱rri brrá nné, ngbe nggwé̱ re-prristi, ngbe nné mie̱ Nti Nka ré ki ra he̱rri ré ki yhwe̱. Me̱di we̱ ci rotu wetsie̱ wire we̱ cinga deze a nhu.
Jesu he nka ne̱ we gbeng. Aha ni Pita ki fie̱ re nzhi bamba ngu a ne̱ ne ki yhwire.
Me̱di Jesu bra, ngu a ri nné ki zhwe ngu, ngu a ti Pita ne ren he, “Shwo n na rê ewie Shetani!” Ngu a he, “Zhwe hwie nka ngwe̱ ne̱ koo wru nwie Be̱ne̱ we̱, a nyi zhwe hwie nka nneywi.”
Wire ngu a ye rigwe̱ nné ngbe nné ki zhwe ngu re be nwie ngu, ngu a he ne mbe he, “Ko nye̱ ne ngu ce̱ ning zhwe, se re ra rici ngu, re fo gasankwe<RF q=+>fo gasankwe:‘fo gasankwe’ e̱ nyi nke he nneywi re ngwa rici ngu ka re nyi zohu zhwe cinci ka ge̱zhe̱ ne ngu shi ki she. ngu re ning zhwe.<RF q=+><a href="b40.10.38">Mat 10:38</a>; <a href="b42.14.27">Luk 14:27</a>
