Ko nye̱ ne ngu to nshwu nje ngbe nti nka nje a zhwe ze̱ nné ne ko shi ré hung sa rie a mbe we̱, ze̱ nné e̱ngwie̱ ne̱, Kowe Nneywi ri to nshwu ngu ma a zhe ne ngu ri be a yarri grime̱ ꞌBe̱ ngu ngbe re-njeli wiri.”
Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Nje níng ting cence, yá ne mbe yo a he ne̱ koó bi ri hu we̱ se ne mbe ri ri be Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ ne igbe̱.”
Bra ikpe rwe̱<TS3>(<a href="b40.17.1-13">Mat 17:1-13</a>; <a href="b42.9.28-36">Luk 9:28-36</a>)Rotu rritsie̱ wara, Jesu a ko mbe Pita, ngbe Yakubu, ngbe Yohana re nzhi a ya zete ya brra rugu we nggaa mbe. Zhe ne mbe shi miimi ikpe rwe̱ Jesu bra a nyyi mbe.<RF q=+><a href="b61.1.17-18">2Pit 1:17-18</a>
