Á srra mbe e̱ ki rinng he, “Nyi nda ngu ci ne nné mie̱ Nti Nka Musa mbe he se Iliya re ke̱she be wire e̱e̱?”<RF q=+><a href="b39.4.5">Mal 4:5</a>; <a href="b40.11.14">Mat 11:14</a>
