Á be ne Jesu nyyi Rotsu Brrá Nné<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.57-68">Mat 26:57-68</a>; <a href="b42.22.54-55">Luk 22:54-55</a>, <a href="b42.22.63-71">63-71</a>; <a href="b43.18.13-14">Yoh 18:13-14</a>, <a href="b43.18.19-24">19-24</a>)Á be ne Jesu nwie Brra Prristi; ngbe rotsu nggwé̱ re-prristi, ngbe brrá nné, ngbe nné mie̱ Nti Nka á ya mwe miimi.
