Nne bi ruhunzhwe̱<TS3>(<a href="b40.8.1-4">Mat 8:1-4</a>; <a href="b41.1.40-45">Mar 1:40-45</a>)A zhe ne Jesu shi a ya ngwie̱, ya nne ne ruhunzhwe̱ e̱ ki ye yhwe̱ be nwie ngu. Zhe ne ngu ri Jesu, ngu a hu be lielie nwie cwe nva ne ngu he, “Brrabe̱, kundu ngwe̱ shî, ning ci n ci gbingbi ngbe n bra ci wiri.”<RF q=+>Ci wiri:A teede nné Yahudi, kundu nne ngu shi ne ruhunzhwe̱ ko shi wiri na re hung ngwie a Zonggru Be̱ne̱ we̱.
Jesu na va ngu a ki re, ngu a he, “Nje shî, ci gbingbi!” We zhe zunzrru ruhunzhwe̱ e̱ ki we.
