Jesu hu kya ne mbe shi hwieng, ngu a we rinng he, “Aha nda ne nyi shi hwie re-nka a yarri rehwie nyi ni e̱e̱?
Nyi zohu ngu bi rwe̱: ré he, ‘Á re we re-e̱ngwie̱ ngwe̱,’ ka ré he, ‘Cinye̱ ngwe̱ cwo ciee e̱e̱?’
Me̱di nje ce̱ níng ting he Kowe Nneywi<RF q=+>Kowe Nneywi:Jesu yaa ye we rici ngu he “Kowe Nneywi”. Ning bra hwieng a <b>Yá re-nti nka ngbe kya mbe hé.</b> e̱ bi igbe̱ a be ngwie̱ ngbe re we re-e̱ngwie̱,” ngu a he ne nne ruhu nna he, “Nje he ne ngwe̱, deze ngwe̱ fo kpengye ngwe̱ ngwe̱ si ri.” e̱ bi igbe̱ a be ngwie̱ ngbe re we re-e̱ngwie̱,” ngu a he ne nne ruhu nna he, “Nje he ne ngwe̱, deze ngwe̱ fo kpengye ngwe̱ ngwe̱ si ri.”
