Ko bra bi nne ngu kro hwihwi rishi ruto a yarri gure kpe<RF q=+>Gure kpe:Nné Yahudi i shi sa rishi ruto a gure kpe, rishi ruto nna cwo tsie we̱ na gure nna he̱rri we̱ cwo we ni we̱ ya hla. na rening we̱. Kundu ne e nyi ni, rishi ruto nna we̱ tsie, we̱ ho gure nna ngbe we̱ wa be, gure nna we̱ bra ci shweni.
