Jesu a we shing he, “Ko nyi sa hwie yarri krre̱de̱ nyi ho kya ne Dooda ngbe nné ngu mbe i nyi a zhe ne mbe i ho nzhwo we̱ e̱e̱?
Dooda i ngwie a Zonggru Be̱ne̱, ngu a fo cwu yâ wiri na ne se we re-prristi re hung yeng, aa ye, he̱rri aa ngwa nné ngu kpi.”<RF q=+><a href="b3.24.9">Liv 24:9</a><RF q=+><a href="b9.21.1-6">1Sam 21:1-6</a>
