Aawo, ko shi ni we̱! Nje níng ting he se nyi se̱ ywe̱, de̱ ni wo nyi e̱ ci shweni zhwozhwo nyi ma.
Ka nyi hwie he nné shwa ne otu klanva ne brra runo dede a Silo ngu i gu ngu we nyie̱ he̱rri mbe kwi ana, re-e̱ngwie̱ mbe e̱ á ne̱ na ga nné ne mbe srra a Urrushelima a zhwozhwo aa?
Aawo, ko shi ni we̱! Nje he ne nyi he se nyi se̱ ywe̱, de̱ ni wo nyi e̱ ci shweni zhwozhwo nyi ma.”
Nka zhwebe riyhwietsie ne ko ngu ci gbre we̱Ngu a we ti nka zhwebe he, “Ya nne i bi ekwe riyhwietsie ne ngu tsi a nhwie̱n ngu, ngu a ywa ngu ya ri ka aa ci gbre. Koo ya she yankya we̱.
Aha nii, ngu a he ne nnencwuo ngu he, ‘Aa ci re-rie wetsie̱ ne nje cwo kre gbre a ekwe ne̱, me̱di ko bi ko yankya we̱. Ki tsa ngwe̱ zhwu! We̱ dzio ewie e̱ we shweni ni e̱ aha nda?’
“Nne nna ngu a he, ‘Be̱ri, ki we he̱rri yaka rie wa, ngbe n ki cwue̱ n ning ci rivi.
Kundu ngu ri ci gbre a rie ngu cwo be we̱ bi rina, de̱ ni we̱, nzhi e̱ tsa nzhi zhwu.’ ”
Jesu kyia ya ho mbrru a Tung Srra CwuJesu i shi mie̱ nka a ya zonggrung mwe a Tung Srra Cwu,
A bi ya ꞌho mbrru ne rije ki ci rugu teme he̱rri re-rie shwa ne otu klanva. Aa ki krru koo hung yaa cwucwu we̱ ko tsie̱ tsie̱.
Zhe ne Jesu ki ri, aa ki ye re be ncwuee. Ngu a he ne ngu he, “A ho mbrru, á re ti ruhu ngwe̱.”
Ngu a ki gara va. We hwiehwie ngu a yaa na, ngu a deze nwie de Be̱ne̱.
Me̱di nnencwuee na zonggrung mwe e̱ dzio ehwie aha ne Jesu ngu kyia nne a Tung Srra Cwu. Ngu a he ne nneywí he, “A bi rotung nyi cwuo ngbe rritsie̱. Aha nii, nyi be a rotu ana ngbe ré níng kyia, we̱sa ne Otung Srra Cwu!”<RF q=+><a href="b2.20.9-10">Wru 20:9-10</a>; <a href="b5.5.13-14">NNMN 5:13-14</a>
Me̱di Brrabe̱ ki shing he, “Nyi nné brra ronu! Nje he ka ko nye̱ nyi bí nnywa ngu ka nze̱e̱kyi ngu a nru we̱ ya ki ngwa rishi a Tung Srra Cwu a?
Aha ni ma ko bi he ngu mbrru ne̱ ne ngu nyi zhwe Ibrrahin ne Shetani i ki rrwe he̱rri re-rie shwa ne otu klanva ne̱ ngbe re she ci gbingbi ne ruhu ngu a a Tung Srra Cwu we̱ e̱e̱?”
A zhe ne Jesu he ni, ga nné ne mbe ki ra nka á shwe nshwu me̱di rehwie nneywí kla ne re-ankyang hwie̱ nga onu ne ngu nyi.
Nka zhwebe na cwe musta<TS3>(<a href="b40.13.31-32">Mat 13:31-32</a>; <a href="b41.4.30-32">Mar 4:30-32</a>)Wire Jesu we rinng he, “Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ shi rimi? N ning mwa yi ngbe nda?
A shi shi nyi cwe musta ne ya nne ngu tsi a nhwie̱n ngu. A shi tsie̱nzhwu le̱le̱ me̱di aa ci brra ekwe he̱rri re̱mie̱ yi á ning no reri mbe a nvang.”
Nka zhwebe na yisti<TS3>(<a href="b40.13.13">Mat 13:13</a>)Jesu we rinng wa he, “Ma n fo Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ n ning mwa yi ne nda?
A shi shi nyi yisti ne ya mbrru ngu fo ngu ki krre a yarri kwrengyi ntsi felewa wetsie̱, he̱rri aa ci bacia ntsi felewa nna zhwozhwo hru.”
Onusinye shi yhwen<TS3>(<a href="b40.7.13-14">Mat 7:13-14</a>)Jesu grra a brrá re-ngwie̱ ngbe re-nkla re nzhi Urrushelima ne ngu cwo re mie̱ nka.
Ya nne ki rinng he, “Brrabe̱, nyi e̱we̱ nné tsienzhwu ne mbe ri she kyia aa?”Ngu a he ne mbe he,
“Ko nye̱ re nyi kwe̱kwe̱ re ngwie a onusinye na ngu shi yhwen, aha nje níng ting he nné piriri ri kre he mbe ngwie, me̱di koó ri she ngwie we̱.
Be̱ri bi eri ri deze we̱ she̱ onusinye, wire nyi e̱ yo ci re cwe ewie nwie cwe nva he, ‘Brrabe̱, kusu níng kla onusinye.’ Me̱di a ri he ne nyi he, ‘Ko nje níng hu we̱, ka ewie ne nyi níng wru.’
“Wire nyi ri he he, ‘Nzhi i ye re shwe ngbe ne ngwe̱, ngwe̱ bra níng mie̱ nka a ngwie̱ nzhi.’
“Nyi ri ku rana a miimi re ye nnyi a zhe ne nyi ri ri Ibrrahin, ngbe Ishaku ngbe Yakubu ngbe nné ti re̱se̱ng zhwozhwo a yarri Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱, me̱di wé̱ níng zi nyi e̱ a ci.<RF q=+><a href="b40.22.13">Mat 22:13</a>; <a href="b40.25.30">25:30</a>
Nneywí ri wru a nva ze ngbe nva ta ngbe nva arewa ngbe nva kudu re be para a Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.8.11-12">Mat 8:11-12</a>
Cence, a bi nné ne mbe shi merin ne mbe ri hwie̱ nné ncwuee, a bi yá nné mbe shi ncwuee ne mbe ri hwie̱ nné merin ma.”
Jesu dzio ehwie aha Urrushelima<TS3>(<a href="b40.23.37-39">Mat 23:37-39</a>)A zhe ana yá nné Farisi i be nwie Jesu, mbe e̱ he ne ngu he, “Ne̱ nwie ne̱ re nzhi yaka ewie, aha Hirridu ce̱ re yhwe̱.”
Aa we brang he, “Nyi ywa nyi ya he ne Hirridu ca rabrra shi ovu yi ana he, ‘Nje shi yu re-rije ma n kyia nné a cwu ngbe a encwe, wire a otu natsie̱ ma n fro cwuo nje.’
Gbengbe ni ma, se n wara ne ciee nje a cwu ngbe encwe ngbe nyiee, aha ko bi ko ya nne ti re̱se̱ng re hu a ci we̱sa ne a Urrushelima we̱!
“Kei! Nyi nné Urrushelima, nyi nné Urrushelima, nyi ne nyi yhwi nné ti re̱se̱ng, nyi bra ta nné ne e we te nwie nyi ne ngbatsie! Aa ci cwoo maa ne nje ce̱ níng tsu gbengbe shi shi de̱ nngwie̱ ne ngu tsu rewe ngu a tahwie gahaa ngu, me̱di ko nyi shî we̱ e̱e̱!
Nyi ri, Brranyi i nyi e̱ cwo a hwie̱ e̱ hwerri. Nje níng ting he ko nyi bra bi níng ri wa we̱ se nyi ri he, ‘Mwo rina shi a zete nne nke ne ngu be a yarri lo Brrabe̱.’ ”<RF q=+><a href="b19.118.26">Rve 118:26</a>; <a href="b24.22.5">Iri 22:5</a>
Jesu kyia ya nne ruhuA ya Otung Srra Cwu nné Yahudi, Jesu ywa ye yâ a ri ya nnencwuee nné Farisi, nneywí sa riyii a ngu dudu dudu.
A bi ya nne ngu be a nwie Jesu ne nta ngu ngbe nva ngu mbe mwi.
Jesu rin nné hu re̱se̱ Nti Nka Musa ngbe nné Farisi he, “Aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri a yarri Nti Nka ngbe ré kyia nne a Tung Srra Cwu a, ka aawo?”
Me̱di á ci cereng, ngu a pie nne nna ngu a ki kyia, ngu a ki cire.
Wire ngu a we rinng he, “Nyi nye̱ a zetsi nyi ne kundu ngu bi nze̱we ka nnywa a ngu, ne ngu kpe a ruvo a Tung Srra Cwu ngbe ko we̱ wre̱ ne ki ti we hwiehwie we̱ e̱e̱?”
Koó bra hu kya he we̱.
Yaa ci re̱A zhe ne ngu ri nné ice ne mbe be mbe shi kre rewie te̱nte̱ng, ngu a we ti nka zhwebe ne̱, a he:
“Kundu ne e re ye a nwie bikyi nyrra, shi de̱ ngwe̱ be ngwe̱ ya ke̱she srra a nwie te̱nte̱ng we̱, aha kabeya a bi ya nne bi grime̱ re re ne̱ ngwe̱ e̱ ne e ki ye ma.<RF q=+><a href="b20.25.6-7">NNZh 25:6-7</a>
Kishi nne ne ngu níng ye nné wehwie nyi e̱ re be re bra ya he ne ngwe̱ he, ‘Deze ngwe̱ we nne ne̱ ncwu ngwe̱.’ Wire nshwu we̱ re yhwe̱ kaka, se ngwe̱ bra ya kre yaka ewie gbong ngwe̱ ning srra.
Me̱di kundu ne e re ye, ywa ngwe̱ ya srra gbong, aha kundu ne nne bi i bikyi e̱ ngu be we̱ he ne ngwe̱ he, ‘A rwi, deze ngwe̱ ya srra a nwie te̱nte̱ng.’ Wire ngwe̱ e̱ she grime̱ a nyyi ko mbe nye̱ ne mbe shi miimi e̱ fa.
Aha ko nye̱ ne ngu fo rici ngu ze, wé̱ ki ci re̱; ko nye̱ ne ngu ci rici ngu re̱, wé̱ ki fo ze.”
Wire Jesu he ne ꞌbe̱ bi eri nna he, “Kundu ne ngwe̱ shi ye nné a para, ka re nyi te̱ne̱ ka ne̱hin, shi de̱ ngwe̱ ye we rwí ngwe̱, ka re-gimbe ngwe̱, ka nzhwe ngwe̱, ka nné bi ncwé̱ dudu ne ngwe̱ we̱. Kishi á ri re ye ma, re bra ci shi á ning brru re trrang.
Me̱di zhe ne ngwe̱ shi ye nné a para, kre ꞌyiriywé̱ ngbe nnenkú ngbe nnencwué̱,
wire ngwe̱ e̱ she mwo rina. Ko ngbe ne ko mbe shi hung re trrang we̱, Be̱ne̱ ri re trrang a tung deze nné redziee.”
Nka zhwebe na brra para<TS3>(<a href="b40.22.1-10">Mat 22:1-10</a>)Ya ne ngu shi srra a tebrru ho ni, ngu a he ne Jesu he, “Mwo rina shi a zete nne nke ne ngu ri ya ye a para na Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱.”
Jesu a he ne ngu he, “Ya nne ye nné ice we yang ngbe ré be a ya brra para.
A zhe ne e shi níng ce̱ para nna, ngu a te ya ꞌhwie ngu he re ywa re ya ye ga nné ne ngu we ti bikyi nna he, ‘Nyi be, aha ko nda dzie yhwe̱.’
“Ko nye̱ ne e ywa ki ye we̱ ngwa e̱we̱e̱ re-kwili kya ngu ci ne ko shi ngu hung be we̱. Nne na ce̱ucwung he, ‘A nyi we zhe ne ne̱ ne nje se̱ kyie, se nje ywa nje ya ri wire. Kusu ning ngwa zhe.’
“Ya mbe he, ‘A nyi we zhe ne ne̱ ne nje si nnywang kye̱ kaa komo shwa, nje nyia re nzhi we mwa n ri. Kusu ning ngwa zhe.’
“He̱rri ne cwu ya mbe he, ‘A nyi we zhe ne ne̱ ne nje fo mbrru, aha nii ko shi n hung be we̱.’
“ꞌHwie nna a ya ning brru, ngu a ya ti be̱ri ngu kya ne ngu ci. Be̱ri ngu a dzio hwie ngu a he ne ꞌhwie ngu a he, ‘Wre̱ ne ne̱ we hwiehwie re nzhi a yarri ngwie̱ ngwe̱ ya grra a brra re-rê ngbe re-hwrre̱ ngwe̱ kyie̱ ga ꞌyiriywé̱, ngbe nnenkú, ngbe nnencwué̱ ré be.’
“Wire be̱ri ꞌhwie nna he ne ngu wa he, ‘Ywa a re-nkla ngwe̱ ya zhwe re-rê ngbe nhwie̱ rê ngbe ngwe̱ ya ye yaká nné re be, aha eri nje re shî.
Nje níng ting he ko bi ko ya a zetsi brrá nné ne i we ye ana ne ngu ri ye ko yankya a nwie para nje we̱.’ ”
Zhwe Jesu<TS3>(<a href="b40.10.37-38">Mat 10:37-38</a>)A ya otu, rigwe̱ nné e shi zhwe Jesu, zhe ne ngu bra ngu we ri, ngu a he ne mbe he,
“Kundu ko nye̱ ngu ce̱ ning zhwe de̱ ngu ning ce̱ re ne̱ ꞌbe̱ ngu, ngbe de̱ ngu, ngbe mbrru ngu, ngbe e̱we̱e̱ rewe ngu, ngbe re-gimbe ngu ntó ngbe mbrrú, he̱rri ngbe ce ngu we̱, cence ko shi re hung hwie̱ nné ning zhwe we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.10.37">Mat 10:37</a>
Nne ne ko ngu hung fo gasankwe ngu, ngu ning zhwe we̱, koo be re hwie̱ nne ning zhwe we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.10.38">Mat 10:38</a>; <a href="b40.16.24">16:24</a>; <a href="b41.8.34">Mar 8:34</a>; <a href="b42.9.23">Luk 9:23</a>
“Kundu ya nyi hwie no eri, ko ke̱she srra be we̱ ri ncwe̱ ne ngu bi e̱, ka ri ki be ngbe ngu ning ngra runo nna ka de̱ ri ki be we̱ wo ye̱?
Kundu ngu ma we dede ngu ce̱ riti runo wire ko ngu bra no yhwe̱ we̱, ko nye̱ ne ngu shi cie̱ we̱ ki mi,
nwie he, ‘Nyi ri ya nne ne ngu ce̱ runo me̱di koo bra hung frong we̱.’
“Nyi zohu nggwe̱ ne kundu ngu nyia re nzhi cwe ne yaka nggwe̱ ko we̱ ke̱she srra be we̱ ri ka re-shezhi ngu komo shwa ꞌci á ri hung ya kwe̱ ne re-shezhi na rwinko ngu nshwa ci wehwie we̱ ye̱?
Kundu ngu hu he ko ngu ri hung kwe̱ng we̱, we̱ ke̱nce̱ te re nzhi a nwie nggwe̱ nke ncwi e̱ ne mbe shi rê re be aha ngbe mbe cwue̱ nkang srra rina.
Aha nii, ko nye̱ a zetsi nyi ne ngu me̱nkye̱ng we ko nda ngu, ko shi re hung hwie̱ nne ning zhwe we̱.
Ncwua ne ngu dzio<TS3>(<a href="b40.5.13">Mat 5:13</a>; <a href="b41.9.50">Mar 9:50</a>)“Ncwua bi rina, me̱di kundu ngu bru kpikpi ngu, wé̱ ce̱ rimi ré bra ki ci re shi kpikpi e̱ wa?
Ko bi mpe̱ni a ebe ka a rivi ne e tsu we̱, se ré fo ré wa. Ko nye̱ ne ngu bi re-uucwung hong, nde re ho.”
Nka zhwebe na canve ngu bru<TS3>(<a href="b40.18.12-14">Mat 18:12-14</a>)Wire ga nné si gondu<RF q=+>Nne si gondu:Di a <b>Yá re-nti nka ngbe kya mbe hé.</b> ngbe nné e̱ngwie̱ á ne̱ ne she re be dudu ne ngu aha ngbe mbe ho nka ngu. ngbe nné e̱ngwie̱ á ne̱ ne she re be dudu ne ngu aha ngbe mbe ho nka ngu.
Me̱di nné Farisi ngbe nné mie̱ Nti Nka Musa a á ne̱ ne krro nka nwie he, “He̱rri nne ne̱ a sí nné e̱ngwie̱ ne̱ re ye yâ ngbe mbe fang!”<RF q=+><a href="b42.5.29-30">Luk 5:29-30</a>
Jesu a we he nka zhwebe he:
“A nyi nye̱ a zetsi nyi, kundu ngu bi canvé komo nnywa zunzrru ne ya bru, ko we̱ we nshwa krruvaya ne otu krruvaya ana a tsi yi, we̱ kpe kreng se ngu ri she wire wo ye̱?
Kundu ne ngu she, we̱ fo ne rekwi a ritengbraa ngu
re si ri. Wire we̱ ye rwí ngu ngbe nné dudu ne eri ngu, gbengbe we̱ he ne mbe he, ‘Nyi ning she nyi rekwi. Nje she canve nje ne ngu i bru.’
Nje níng ting he a shi ni ma, á ri nyi rekwi we yang a zinye̱ aha nne zunzrru ne ngu se̱ ywe̱ re ne̱ nné redziee komo nshwa krruvaya ne otu krruvaya ne ko mbe bra bi nkang se̱ ywe̱ we̱.
Nka zhwebe na mbrru ngu bru cwe azrrufa“Ka nyi zohu mbrru ne ngu bi cwe azrrufa komo shwang ne ya bru, ko we̱ ci ro fitile̱, we̱ ko ewie a ri ngu nwie kreng wesheng wesheng we̱ e̱e̱?
Kundu ngu she, we̱ ye re-ꞌla ngu ngbe nné dudu ne eri ngu gbengbe, we̱ he, ‘Nyi ning she nyi rekwi. Nje she cwe ncwe̱ azrrufa nje ne ngu ri bru.’
A shi ni ma, nje níng ting, a bi rekwi a nyyi re-njeli Be̱ne̱ aha nne e̱ngwie̱ zunzrru ne ngu se̱ ywe̱.”
Nka zhwebe na ewenwuJesu ning brang he, “Ya nne bi zrre̱we wehwie.
Iishi nna ngu a he ne ꞌbe̱ ngu he, ‘ꞌBe̱, níng kye dukyie̱e̱ ngwe̱, ngbe ngwe̱ ning ngwa na nje.’ ꞌBe̱ nna a we kyeng.
“Á srra yá e̱wé̱ rotu tsie̱, iishi nze̱we nna a tsu re-ankya ngu zhwozhwo, ngu a nyi ciee re nzhi ya ngwie̱ gbong. Aa ya srra nwie nyi wu, aa se̱ dukyie̱e̱ ngu yhwe̱ wiriri.
A zhe ne ngu ye ko nda ngu yhwe̱ fa, wire ya brra nzhwo kpe a ngwie̱ nna. Riywe̱ ki pie.
Aa ne̱ ya kre cwuo a nwie ya nne ngwie̱ nna. Nne nna a ki fo ncwuo cwo re-lede a yi.<RF q=+>Cwo re-lede:A nwie nné Yahudi, lede e̱ nyi kya le̱le̱. Koó ye we̱ wire re ning hwie̱ brong (Liv 11:7-8).
A ce̱ he ngu ra she fenfe yâ re-lede ngu ye, me̱di ko bi ya nne ngu ki ngwa we̱.
Nje shi deze a he ne̱ n ning brru re nzhi nwie ꞌbe̱ nje, ma n ya he ne ngu he: ꞌBe̱, nje nyi Be̱ne̱ e̱ngwie̱, nje bra re nyi e̱ngwie̱ ma.
A zhe ne ko nje be he ré bra ning ye he ewe ngwe̱ wa we̱. Ning fo n hwie̱ shi ya ꞌhwie ngwe̱.’
“Ngu a deze ngu a ning brru re nzhi nwie ꞌbe̱ ngu.“We zhe ne ngu shi we gbong, ꞌbe̱ ngu ki ri, naana ki pie ngu a rwi ta be re nzhi nyi ne ngu, ngu a ya ki krru ngu a ki me ushwo.
“Ewe nna he ne ngu he, ‘ꞌBe̱, nje nyi Be̱ne̱ e̱ngwie̱, nje bra re nyi e̱ngwie̱ ma. Ko nje be ré bra cinga ning ye he ewe ngwe̱ wa we̱.’
Me̱di ꞌbe̱ nna he ne hwié e ngu he, ‘Nyi cwo wehwie nyi be mi ne brra te̱nte̱ tago hwi nyi ki cing, nyi ki ci ewema a nva ngbe tamri a nta.
Nyi be mi ne ngba wu izhimi ana nyi cie̱ ngbe nzhi ye re nyi rekwi,
aha kowe nje ne̱ i hu, a bra shi nce; a i bru, á bra ki she.’ Ngbe mbe e̱ ne̱ ne nyi re-rekwi.
“A zhe ana, ꞌho nze̱we nna ywa yi, a cwo re be ri. A zhe ne ngu be dudu ne eri ngu a ho ne e cwe re-ankya re shwo rocwu.
Aa ye ya ꞌhwie, ngu a ki rinng he, ‘Nyi nda ne e shi mi he e̱e̱?’
“ꞌHwie e̱ ki shing he, ‘Nyi iishi ngwe̱ ngu be ri, kya a nyi ngwiee ne ꞌbe̱ ngwe̱ ki cie̱ ngba wu izhimi ana, aha aa be ri rina rina.’
“ꞌHo nze̱we nna a dzio ehwie, he̱rri a ra ngwie e ri. ꞌBe̱ ngu a wru, ngu a ya ne̱ ne ki krru ehwie.
Me̱di aa ki karang he, ‘Di, ga re-rie ne̱ nje re nyi cwuo shi ya ꞌhwie, ko nje sa ra nyi yankya ne ngwe̱ he n nyi we̱. Me̱di ko ngwe̱ re ning ngwa ko ve ngbe n cie̱ n ning rre ngbe rwí nje we̱.
Me̱di a zhe ne ewenwu ngwe̱ ne̱ ngu ya yhwe̱ dukyie̱e̱ ngwe̱ we shweni a nwie ntsie̱wenté ngu be ri, ngwe̱ ki cie̱ ngba wu izhimi!’
“ꞌBe̱ nna a he ne ngu he, ‘Ewe nje, ko zohu zhe ngwe̱ ne̱ ngwe̱ shi ngbe ne nje. Ko nda ne nje bi nyi na ngwe̱.
Me̱di aa ye nzhi nyi rekwi ne ehwie kla aha gimbe ngwe̱ ne̱. A i hu, me̱di a zhe ne ne̱ a shi nce; aa ki bru, me̱di nzhi ki she.’ ”
Nka zhwebe nnencwuo ye nné ne leJesu he ne nné ki zhwe ngu he, “A bi ya nne bi va ne ngu fo ya nne re hwie̱ nne ki ci nkwile̱ ne re-cwuo ngu. Á ki ting he nne nna sé̱ dukyie̱e̱ ngu we dede.
A zhe ne ngu ki ye, a ki rinng he, ‘Nyi nda ne nje ho a rici ngwe̱ he ni e̱e̱? Ning hwie nhwie̱ ne ngwe̱ ning cwo mi ne cwuo nje e̱, aha nje shi re ti ncwuo.’
“Nnencwuo nna ngu a yaa rinng we rici ngu he, ‘Ma, a zhe ne ne̱ nyi nda ne nje shi nying? Be̱ri nje e̱ nyi nke ngu shi ning ti ncwuo ne. Ko nje bi igbe̱ n ning kye̱ kaa we̱. A bra nyi kya nshwu n ne̱ ne gye̱ re ce̱ ankya.
E̱nhe̱n! Nje hu kya ne nje shi nying fa ngbe nneywí ri ning se̱ a reri mbe, kundu ne e ri ning yu ncwuo.’
“Aa ye ko zohu nne bi tsie be̱ri ngu. A rin nne na ce̱ucwung he, ‘A nyi tsie nda ne be̱ri nje e̱ re zhwe?’
Aa ki shing he, ‘Nyi re-grre̱we̱n remie nnywa zunzrru.’“Nnencwuo nna a he ne ngu he, ‘Ning ge krre̱de̱. Wie he nyi re-grre̱we̱n nshwa wecwuoo.’
Ngu a rin nne na ꞌhwie he, ‘Ngwe̱ e̱ rre, nyi wema ne e re zhwe?’ Ngu a he, ‘Á ning zhwe re-katanko alikama nnywa zunzrru.’ Nnencwuo nna a he ne ngu he, ‘Ning ge krre̱de̱ ngwe̱. Wie he nyi re-katanko nshwa klanva.’
Be̱ri ngu a be ya ki de aha zhwe zentsi ne ngu bi. Aha nné tsi ngwie̱ ne̱ á bi zentsing cwo ne ankya ngwie̱ ne̱ re ne̱ nné na ewie si.”
