Aa ye hwié ngu ngbe shwa ngu a ngwa ko nye̱ tsi mbe ncwe̱ ne ngu be ré ning trra nnencwuó he̱rri nyhwe̱ wetsie̱, ngu a he ne mbe he, ‘Nyi fo ncwe̱ ne̱ nyi ka brrang ne nje cwo a ning brru.’
“Me̱di ko nné ngu a á ki ce̱ we̱, mbe e̱ te yá nné a merin ngu ngbe ré ya he he, ‘Ko nzhi ce̱ nne ne̱ re hwie̱ nggwe̱ nzhi we̱.’
“Gbengbe ni, á ki ngwa ringgwe̱ nna, ngu a ning brru re be ri. Ngu a te ne hwié ngu ne ngu ri we ngwa ncwe̱ e̱ he ré be mi ngbe ngu ri kya ne ko nye̱ mbe ngu ning sheng a zeteng.
Nne na ce̱ucwung be ngu a he, ‘Be̱ri, ncwe̱ ne ngwe̱ ning ngwa a ngra ce shwang.’
Be̱ri ngu a he ne ngu he, ‘Te̱nte̱ ni, ꞌhwie rina nje! Aha ngwe̱ bi redziee a e̱we̱ kya tsienzhwu, nje re ngwa ringgwe̱ brrá re-ngwie̱ shwang.’
Nne na ꞌhwie e be ngu a he, ‘Be̱ri, ncwe̱ ne ngwe̱ ning ngwa n brra a ngra ce ꞌcwuoo.’
Be̱ri ngu a he, ‘Nje re ngwa ringgwe̱ brrá re-ngwie̱ wecwuoo.’
“Wire na ꞌtsie̱ e̱ be ma ngu a he, ‘Be̱ri, ri ncwe̱ ngwe̱ e̱ nyi nke, nje fo nje ki rwe a yarri kla trro nje sa.
Nje to owu ngwe̱, aha ngwe̱ bi rwe̱. Nje hu he ngwe̱ kre we ankya shweni, ngwe̱ ca yâ ne ko ngwe̱ kye̱ we̱.’
“Be̱ri ngu a he ne ngu he, ‘Nje shi re nyi nka aha nka nu ngwe̱, ngwe̱ ꞌhwie bi ꞌhwie̱! Ngwe̱ hu he nje bi rwe̱, nje kre we ankya shweni, nje ca yâ ne ko nje kye̱ we̱.
Aha nda ne ko ngwe̱ sa ncwe̱ nje e̱ a benkyi, ngbe nje ri ya ning brru n ya she rruba a zeteng we̱ e̱e̱?’
“Mbe e̱ ki shing he, ‘Be̱ri, nje he ka a bi shwang ye̱ e̱e̱!’
“Ngu a he, ‘Nje níng ting he ko nye̱ ne ngu bi, á ri ki brang piriri; me̱di nne ne ko ngu bi ko yankya we̱, ngbe e̱we̱ kya ne ngu bi e̱, á ri se̱ a nva ngu.<RF q=+><a href="b40.13.12">Mat 13:12</a>; <a href="b41.4.25">Mar 4:25</a>; <a href="b42.8.18">Luk 8:18</a>
Me̱di rwinkó nje ne ko mbe ce̱ he n hwie̱ nggwe̱ mbe ana we̱, nyi be ne mbe he nyi we yhwi a nyyi nje.’ ”
Jesu ngwie a Urrushelima we dengge<TS3>(<a href="b40.21.1-11">Mat 21:1-11</a>; <a href="b41.11.1-11">Mar 11:1-11</a>; <a href="b43.12.12-19">Yoh 12:12-19</a>)A zhe ne Jesu ngu he nka ni, ngu a wara re nzhi a Urrushelima.
Zhe ne ngu cwo re be dudu ne Betefaji ngbe Betani, re-nkla ne mbe shi dudu ne Rugu Bi Rekwe Rihwie̱n, aa te yá nné ki zhwe ngu wehwie
he, “Nyi ywa a nkla ne ngu shi ncwuee nyi ana. A zhe ne nyi ri ngwie, nyi e̱ ri ya e̱we̱ nze̱e̱kyi ne e ki rwe miimi, ne ko ya nne sa ning ngra we̱. Nyi ki bi nyi be mi he.
Kundu ya nne níng rinng he, ‘Nyi shi bing aha nda aa?’ Nyi he ne ngu he, ‘Brrabe̱ ce̱.’<RF q=+>Brrabe̱ ce̱:A krre̱de̱ na nka Heleni, á wie heBrrabe̱ bing ce̱. Ri ntsa 19:34 wa.”
Nné ne e we te e̱, á ywa á ya timi a shi we shi ne ngu ri we heng.
A zhe ne mbe shi bing, nné ne mbe bi nze̱e̱kyi nna á we rinng he, “Aha nda nyi shi bi nze̱e̱kyi ne̱?”
Á we shing he, “Brrabe̱ ce̱.”
Á be mi ne nze̱e̱kyi nna nwie Jesu, mbe e̱ ning ta re-ankya ci rwe̱ mbe a zeteng, wire mbe e̱ fo Jesu mbe e̱ ki gara a zeteng.
A zhe ne ngu shi ciee, nneywí ne̱ ne ta re-ankya ci rwe̱ mbe a rê.
A zhe ne ngu be dudu ne gasire ngu ka ngu wro a Rugu Bi Rekwe Rihwie̱n re nzhi Urrushelima, rigwe̱ nné ne mbe shi ki zhwe á ne̱ ne nyi rekwi re de Be̱ne̱ ne cwue ze aha re-ankyang nga onu ne mbe ri.
Á he,“Mwo rina nyi ngge ngu ne ngu be a yarri lo Brrabe̱!Srra rina zinye̱ be nwie nzhi,nzhi ngwa Brrabe̱ grime̱!”<RF q=+><a href="b19.118.26">Rve 118:26</a>
Yá nné Farisi a yarri rigwe̱ nné e̱ he ne Jesu he, “Nne Mie̱ Nka, yhwire nné re zhwe ngwe̱ ne̱ ngbe ré dzie̱ cereng.”
Jesu he ne mbe he, “Nje níng ting, kundu mbe ci cereng, ko we rahwan wé̱ ne̱ ne ti nku.”
A zhe ne ngu sa dudu ne Urrushelima ngu ri ngwie̱ nna, ngu a ti reyii aha ngwie̱ nna.
Ngu a he, “Ka! A cwu ne̱, shi nyi ra hu kya ne ngu shi níng be mi ne srra rina! Me̱di a zhe ne ne̱, ko nyi ri we̱.
Rotu nna cwo be ne rwinkó nyi ri no re-garru ngbe wé̱ níng grra wé̱ níng ci zetsi ko zohu eme.
Á ri níng ywrru ré níng kro be ré níng yhwi ngbe e̱we̱e̱ rewe nyi a yarring. Koó ri we ya ngbaatsie a zete ya we̱, aha ko nyi shî he Be̱ne̱ e̱ be ya níng kyia we̱.”
Jesu a Brranyi<TS3>(<a href="b40.21.12-17">Mat 21:12-17</a>; <a href="b41.11.15-19">Mar 11:15-19</a>; <a href="b43.2.13-22">Yoh 2:13-22</a>)Wire ngu a ngwie a yarri Brranyi ngu a ne̱ ne yu nné mbe shi rie̱ ankya.
Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Á wie he, ‘Eri nje e̱ ri hwie̱ zonggrung ku Be̱ne̱,’ me̱di nyi ki fo aa hwie̱ brra rieng srra nnencá!”<RF q=+><a href="b23.56.7">Ish 56:7</a>; <a href="b24.7.11">Iri 7:11</a>
Ko zohu otu a mie̱ nka a Brranyi, me̱di nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nné mie̱ nti nka Musa ngbe nnencwueé á kre rê he mbe ki yhwe̱.<RF q=+><a href="b42.21.37">Luk 21:37</a>
Me̱di koó she rê mbe ki yhwe̱ we̱, aha ga nné zhwozhwo á zhwe nka ngu.
Á rin Jesu nka aha de̱me̱ ngu<TS3>(<a href="b40.21.23-27">Mat 21:23-27</a>; <a href="b41.11.27-33">Mar 11:27-33</a>)A ya otu ne Jesu shi mie̱ nné nka a yarri Brranyi re brro Nka Rina, nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nné mie̱ Nti Nka Musa ngbe brrá nné á be nwie ngu.
Á he ne ngu he, “Ngwe̱ she de̱me̱ ne ngwe̱ ning nyi re-cwuo ne̱ a he? Nyi nye̱ ngu re ngwa de̱me̱ng nyi re-cwuo ne̱?”
A he ne mbe he, “Ma nde n níng rin nka ma. Nyi ning ting,
de̱me̱ ne Yohana ngu i ning nyi batisma i wru nwie Be̱ne̱ ka nwie nneywí?”
Á ne̱ ne yaa rin re-nka a nci mbe he, “Kundu nzhi ri he aa wru nwie Be̱ne̱, we̱ níng rinng he ma nyi nda ngu ci ne ko nzhi se̱ nka ngu we̱ e̱ ye̱?
Aha nii, mbe e̱ he ne Jesu he, “Ko nzhi hu ka de̱me̱ ngu a i wru he we̱.”
Jesu a he ne mbe he, “Ko shi n níng ting ka nyi nye̱ ngu ning ngwa de̱me̱ ne nje ning nyi re-cwuo ne̱ ma we̱.”
Nka zhwebe yá nné kaa<TS3>(<a href="b40.21.33-46">Mat 21:33-46</a>; <a href="b41.12.1-12">Mar 12:1-12</a>)Ngu a wara ne we ti nka zhwebe he: “Ya nne kye̱ inebi<RF q=+>Inebi:Di a <b>Yá re-nti nka ngbe kya mbe hé.</b> a yarri nhwie̱n ngu, ngu a ngwa yá nné kaa ne mbe ri ma ki trrang, wire ngu a nyi ciee ne ngu shi ya ci zhe we yang.<RF q=+><a href="b23.5.1">Ish 5:1</a> a yarri nhwie̱n ngu, ngu a ngwa yá nné kaa ne mbe ri ma ki trrang, wire ngu a nyi ciee ne ngu shi ya ci zhe we yang.<RF q=+><a href="b23.5.1">Ish 5:1</a>
A zhe ne ngbre inebi nna a ya ci kpi, ngu a te ya ꞌhwie ngu a nwie nné ne ngu we ngwa ebe nna aha re ya ki kpi yá ngbre inebi nna. Me̱di nné nna á ya cwe ꞌhwie nna, á ki cire ne nva hwerri.
Aa cinga te yaka ꞌhwie. Nke e̱ wa, á ya ki cwe, á ki ci nshwu, á ning brru mi ne ngu ne nva hwerri.
He̱rri ne cwu, aa te ꞌhwie na tsie̱ wawa, á ki ci ruhu á ki zhwu ci.
Wire be̱ri bi nhwie̱n inebi nna he, ‘Nje shi nyi rimi ne̱? Nje shi te ewe ce̱ nje, kabeya ré ya to riyii ngu.’
Me̱di zhe ne nné ne ngu we ngwa ebe nna mbe ki ri we ri, á wre̱ ne rwe nka he, ‘Nke e̱ nyi ngu ngu nyi ewe ye gado nna, nyi ning be nzhi ki yhwe̱ ngbe ankya nna ré hwie̱ ngge nzhi.’
Aha nii, mbe e̱ ki ti ci a yarri nhwie̱n nna, wire mbe e̱ ki yhwe̱.“Ma nyi hwie nyi nda ne nne bi nhwie̱n ne̱ ri we nying?
Ko ri be we̱ ya we yhwi, ngbe we̱ ngwa yaká nné nhwie̱n nna we̱ e̱e̱?”A zhe ne nné mbe ho ni, mbe e̱ he, “Ka! Shi de̱ re ci ni we̱!”
Jesu we di te̱nte̱ ngu a we rinng he, “Ma nka ne e wie a yarri Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ ne̱ he rimi? Ne e wie he,‘Ngbaatsie ne nné runo mbe ra,nyi nke ngu hwie̱ ꞌte̱nte̱ng.’<RF q=+><a href="b19.118.22">Rve 118:22</a>
Ko nye̱ ne ngu grre̱ a ngbaatsie ana we̱ yaa kprre, me̱di nne nke ne ngbaatsie ana a kpe a zete ngu we̱ ki mle̱ she̱she̱.”
Trra gondu<TS3>(<a href="b40.22.15-22">Mat 22:15-22</a>; <a href="b41.12.13-17">Mar 12:13-17</a>)Nné mie̱ Nti Nka Musa ngbe nggwé̱ re-prristi e̱ á ne̱ ne kre rê ngbe mbe ki pie we hwiehwie, aha á hu he Jesu he nka zhwebe ne̱ a rici mbe. Me̱di á to owu nné.
Á ne̱ ne ning sa riyii ngu dudu. Á te yá nné ne mbe tiyi shi mbe nyi ꞌte̱nte̱ nné re grra ranranng, aha ne mbe sa rie he mbe shi ki pie a ya nka ne ngu shi heng, ngbe mbe ki ngwa a nva goona ne ngu bi de̱me̱ re ki nyi nka.
Aha nii, nné ne e we te e̱ á rin Jesu nka á he, “Nne Mie̱ Nka, nzhi hu he ko nda ne ngwe̱ he ngbe ne ankya ne ngwe̱ mie̱ á shi ye̱ye̱rri, ko ngwe̱ bra ce̱ rici we̱, me̱di ngwe̱ mie̱ nné rê Be̱ne̱ ye̱ye̱rri ne nka raywrra.
