“Nde n ri cwe ncwe̱ nna, nyi foto nye̱ ngbe lo nye̱ ngu shi a zete ncwe̱ ne̱?”Mbe e̱ shî he, “Nyi Brra Nggwe̱ Rroma.”
Ngu a he ne mbe he, “Aha ni nyi ngwa Brra Nggwe̱ Rroma kya ngu nyi na ngu, nyi bra ngwa Be̱ne̱ kya ngu nyi na Be̱ne̱.”
Á me̱nkye̱ng ki pie a kya ne ngu he a nyyi nneywí, á ne̱ ne nye̱ ronu aha re-shî nka ne ngu we shing, he̱rri á dzie̱ cereng.
Deze a nhu ngbe nyrra<TS3>(<a href="b40.22.23-33">Mat 22:23-33</a>; <a href="b41.12.18-27">Mar 12:18-27</a>)Yá nné Sadukyi<RF q=+>Nné Sadukyi:Di a <b>Yá re-nti nka ngbe kya mbe hé.</b> ne mbe he he ko bi deze nhu we̱, á be nwie Jesu, á ki rinng he,<RF q=+><a href="b44.23.8">RNné 23:8</a> ne mbe he he ko bi deze nhu we̱, á be nwie Jesu, á ki rinng he,<RF q=+><a href="b44.23.8">RNné 23:8</a>
“Nne Mie̱ Nka, Musa i níng wieng he kundu gimbe ya nne hu we mbrru ngu we̱sa ne ewe, ngu nne nna we̱ fo kpambrru gimbe ngu a, aha re she rewe ne lo gimbe ngu.<RF q=+><a href="b5.25.5">NNMN 25:5</a>
A i bi yá re-gimbe komo natsie̱. Nne na ce̱ucwung fo mbrru me̱di aa hu we̱sa she ewe.
