Be Kowe Nneywi na ꞌhwie<TS3>(<a href="b40.24.29-31">Mat 24:29-31</a>; <a href="b41.13.24-27">Mar 13:24-27</a>)“A ri bi yá re-ankyang hwie̱ nga onu a ꞌne̱, ngbe yhwe̱, ngbe re̱nde̱. A be ngwie̱, nneywí a re-ngwie̱ ri ci rowu aha brrá re-nzhwo rishi i ri yhwi nwie kpe ru.<RF q=+><a href="b23.13.10">Ish 13:10</a>; <a href="b26.32.7">Ezi 32:7</a>; <a href="b29.2.31">Yow 2:31</a>; <a href="b66.6.12-13">RYoh 6:12-13</a>
