Wire wé̱ ri Kowe Nneywi ngu ya wre̱ re be a yarri inyie̱ ne igbe̱ ngbe grime̱ we yang.<RF q=+><a href="b27.7.13">Dan 7:13</a>; <a href="b66.1.7">RYoh 1:7</a>
A zhe ne re-ankya ne̱ ri ne̱ ne ci, nyi deze nyi bra yo gangga aha kyia nyi e̱ sa dudu.”
Jesu mie̱ nka ne riyhwietsie<TS3>(<a href="b40.24.32-35">Mat 24:32-35</a>; <a href="b41.13.28-31">Mar 13:28-31</a>)Aa we ti nka zhwebe ne̱ he, “Nyi ri ekwe riyhwietsie ngbe rekwe zhwozhwo.
A zhe ne mbe ne̱ ne yhwu rohun, nyi hung ding ne nyyi nyi he̱rri nyi hu he zhe rikwi i be dudu.
Aha nii, kundu nyi ri di re-ankya ne̱ mbe shi ci, nyi hu he Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ sa dudu.
“Nje níng ting cence, ko nné nze̱ ne̱ e̱ shi kwi yhwe̱ we̱ se re-ankya ne̱ zhwozhwo mbe ci.
Zinye̱ ngbe ebe ngwie̱ shi yhwe̱, me̱di ko nti nka nje bi ci shweni we̱.
Mie̱ nka aha srrante“Nyi nyi te̱nte̱, shi de̱ nyi ngwa rehwie nyi nwie ye re shwe re-ankyang dzio nci ngbe ankyang ho shwi ebe ngwie̱ he̱rri otu tuuye re ya níng hu kprikpri
we̱sa ne srrante we̱. Aha a cwo be a zete nneywí zhwozhwo ne mbe srra ko he a be ngwie̱.
Ko zohu zhe nyi srrante re ku Be̱ne̱ ngbe nyi ri she nyi to nyi drre̱ re-nzhwe ankya ne mbe ri ci, aha ngbe nyi she nyi yo a nyyi Kowe Nneywi.”
Ko zohu otu, Jesu cwo mie̱ nka a Brranyi, ko zohu ne̱hin we̱ wru re nzhi kywe a Rugu Bi Rekwe Rihwie̱n.
A brra mincwe nneywí zhwozhwo cwo nwie ngu a Brranyi aha mbe ho re-nka ngu.
Á rwe nkang pie Jesu<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.1-5">Mat 26:1-5</a>; <a href="b41.14.1-2">Mar 14:1-2</a>; <a href="b43.11.45-53">Yoh 11:45-53</a>)A zhe ne Para Brredi We̱sa Yisti i be dudu, ne e ki ye he Para Paska.<RF q=+>Para Paska:Ri Teede Paska a <b>Yá re-nti nka ngbe kya mbe hé.</b><RF q=+><a href="b2.12.1-27">Wru 12:1-27</a><RF q=+><a href="b2.12.1-27">Wru 12:1-27</a>
Nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nné mie̱ Nti Nka Musa mbe e̱ ne̱ ne kre re-rê ne mbe shi ning yhwe̱ Jesu a la la, aha ne mbe to owu nné ne mbe shi miimi.
Yahuda a shî he ngu shi rie̱ Jesu<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.14-16">Mat 26:14-16</a>; <a href="b41.14.10-11">Mar 14:10-11</a>)Shetani e̱ ngwie a yarri Yahuda ne e ki ye he Iskarriyoti ne ngu nyi ya a tsi nné zhwe Jesu shwa ne otu wehwie.
Ngu a wre̱ ne ne̱ re nzhi rwe nka ngbe nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nnencwueé nné cwo Brranyi re̱se̱ rê ngu shi we rie̱ Jesu.
Á nyi rekwi we yang, mbe e̱ shî he mbe shi ki trra ncwe̱.
Aha nii, Yahuda a shî, ngu a ne̱ ne kre rê ngu we ngwa Jesu ne ko nneywí mbe ru we̱.
Jesu ye yâ Para Paska<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.17-25">Mat 26:17-25</a>; <a href="b41.14.12-21">Mar 14:12-21</a>; <a href="b43.13.21-30">Yoh 13:21-30</a>)A zhe ne otu Parang Ye Brredi We̱sa Yisti i be, ne e shi ca canvé na Para Paska,
Jesu te mbe Pita ngbe Yohana, a he ne mbe he, “Nyi ywa nyi ya nyi yâ Paska ngbe nzhi ye.”
Á ki rinng he, “Ngwe̱ ce̱ he nzhi ya nyi a he?”
A he ne mbe he, “We zhe ne nyi ri ngwie a ngwie̱ Urrushelima, ya nne ne ngu kpe ondrro rishi cwo a nyi ne nyi, nyi ki zhwe re nzhi ri ne ngu shi ning ngwie.
We̱ níng ti ya brra zonggru zeteng ne e ning ta ankya, nyi e̱ nyi ko nda a miimi.”
Á wre̱ ne ne̱ re nzhi, á ya she ko nda shi we ye̱ye̱rri shi kya ne Brrabe̱ he ne mbe, mbe e̱ nyi yâ Para Paska a miimi.
Ye bikyi Brrabe̱<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.26-30">Mat 26:26-30</a>; <a href="b41.14.22-26">Mar 14:22-26</a>; <a href="b46.11.23-25">1Kor 11:23-25</a>)Ne zhe ngu ya cwu, Jesu ya srra be a gumong ye yâ ngbe nnenté ngu.
A he ne mbe he, “Nje ce̱ he nje ra ye yâ Para Paska ne̱ ngbe ne nyi wire n shwe ge̱zhe̱.
Nje níng ting he, ko nje bra bi ye bikyi ne̱ engbe ne nyi wa we̱, se we a tu ne ngu ri ya ci rrurru ni a yarri Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱.”
A zhe ne ngu fo kwrreshi, ngu a ci Be̱ne̱ kijie̱ng, ngu a he, “Nyi ning ge nyi yaa kyeng.
Nje níng ting cence he ko nje bra bi shwe rishi ruto ne̱ ngbe ne nyi wa we̱ se Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ ri be.”
Wire ngu a fo brredi. Re̱se̱ ne ngu ci Be̱ne̱ kijie̱ng, ngu a hwin ngu a we ngwa nwie he ne mbe he, “Nke ne̱ nyi rwe̱ nje ne e ngwa aha nyi, nyi srra re yeng re lu aha nje.”
A merin nke aa fo kwrreshi rishi ruto, a he, “Kwrreshi ne̱ a nyi na ꞌjee hwi ne Be̱ne̱ e̱ níng sang, á nyi ne roshwo nje ne ngu shi wa aha nyi.<RF q=+><a href="b24.31.31-34">Iri 31:31-34</a>
Me̱di nyi ri, va nne ne ngu shi ning rie̱ e̱ a shi yarri enjie yâ engbe na nje!<RF q=+><a href="b19.41.9">Rve 41:9</a>
Cence, Kowe Nneywi e̱ shi hu ye̱ye̱rri ne Be̱ne̱ i he, me̱di wuhu ne nne ngu ki rie̱!”
Nné ki zhwe ngu á ne̱ ne yaa rin re-nka we nci mbe he ma a nyi nye̱ a tsi mbe ne ngu shi nyi zhwe ngge ne̱.
Nyi nye̱ ngu nyi brrangOnu ce e̱ deze a tsi mbe he ka nyi nye̱ ne ngu shi hwie̱ brrang ye̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.18.1">Mat 18:1</a>; <a href="b41.9.34">Mar 9:34</a>; <a href="b42.9.46">Luk 9:46</a>
Jesu he ne mbe he, “Nggwé̱ nné tsi ngwie̱ á ti nné mbe he mbe bi igbe̱ a zete rici mbe, nnencwueé mbe e̱ á bra ce̱ he re we ye he ‘Nné She Nneywíng.’<RF q=+><a href="b40.20.25-27">Mat 20:25-27</a>; <a href="b41.10.42-44">Mar 10:42-44</a>
Me̱di shi de̱ re shi ni a tsi nyi we̱. Nne nke ne ngu nyi brrang a tsi nyi re hwie̱ shi ngu nyi iishing; nnencwuee a tsi nyi re hwie̱ shi ngu nyi ꞌhwie.<RF q=+><a href="b40.23.11">Mat 23:11</a>; <a href="b41.9.35">Mar 9:35</a>
Nyi nye̱ ngu nyi brrang, nyi nne nke ne ngu srra be nwie ye yâ aa, ka nne nke ne ngu shi ncwuong kye yâ? Ko nyi nne nke ne ngu srra be nwie yeng we̱ e̱e̱? Me̱di nje shi tsi nyi he ne̱ shi nyi nnencwuo kye yâ.<RF q=+><a href="b43.13.12-15">Yoh 13:12-15</a>
“A nyi nyi ne̱ ne nyi yaa rwe nyi yo ngbe nje a re-mwa ri nje.
We shi shi ne ꞌBe̱ nje ngu ning ngwa ye ringgwe̱, nje níng ngwa ma.
Nyi ri ye nyi shwe ngbe nje a gumo nje a Ringgwe̱ nje. Nyi ri srra a ncwú ringgwe̱ re ye ringgwe̱ re-nkla shwa ne otu wehwie na rewe Isrreela.<RF q=+><a href="b40.19.28">Mat 19:28</a>
Pita ri klo ne hu Jesu<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.31-35">Mat 26:31-35</a>; <a href="b41.14.27-31">Mar 14:27-31</a>; <a href="b43.13.36-38">Yoh 13:36-38</a>)“Sima, Sima! Di! Shetani i rin Be̱ne̱ he ngu níng mwa ri zhwozhwo nyi shi shi shwunshwu alikama ne e klo.
Me̱di nje ku Be̱ne̱ aha ngwe̱ Pita, kishi sa rie ngwe̱ e̱ ri re̱. Zhe ne ngwe̱ ri ning brru re be nwie nje, ngwe̱ shwe̱ re-gimbe ngwe̱ e̱ rehwie ma.”
Pita a ki shing he, “Brrabe̱, nje yaa rwe he n re zhwe he̱rri uucwu gyiaa, ka ri bra nyi hu ma ho!”
Jesu he ne ngu he, “Pita, nje re ting he, kya ngu pie a totu cwu ne̱, koó ri ma ne ꞌgba tsie̱ we̱, ngwe̱ ri klo he ko ngwe̱ ning hu we̱ ce ꞌtsie̱.”
Jesu a we rin nka he, “A zhe ne nje i níng te we̱sa ne lente ncwe̱, ka brra lente yâ, we̱sa ne tamri wa, nyi ki kre yankya wenywa aa?”<RF q=+><a href="b40.10.9-10">Mat 10:9-10</a>; <a href="b41.6.8-9">Mar 6:8-9</a>; <a href="b42.9.3">Luk 9:3</a>; <a href="b42.10.4">10:4</a>Á he ne ngu he, “Aawo, Brrabe̱.”
Wire ngu a he ne mbe he, “Me̱di a zhe ne ne̱, nne ne ngu bi lente ncwé̱ re fo, nne ngu bi lenteng ci yâ re fo, nne de̱ ngu bi ise̱nkeli we̱ re rie̱ kuntu ngu re ning se̱ ya.
Nje níng ting he riti nka Be̱ne̱ ne e wie he, ‘Á ki hwie a tsi nné e̱ngwie̱ e̱,’ se ngu ci rrurru a rici nje. Ee! Kya ne e wie a rici nje e̱ a shi ci rrurru.”<RF q=+><a href="b23.53.12">Ish 53:12</a>
Wire nné ki zhwe ngu a á he ne ngu he, “Brrabe̱, di nzhi bi re-ise̱nkeli komo wehwie a he ne̱.”A he ne mbe he, “Mbe ana á be.”
Jesu ya ku Be̱ne̱ a Rugu Rekwe Rihwie̱n<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.36-46">Mat 26:36-46</a>; <a href="b41.14.32-42">Mar 14:32-42</a>)Jesu wru re nzhi Rugu Rekwe Rihwie̱n shi ne ngu ning mrrang. Nné ki zhwe ngu a á ki zhwe re nzhi.
A zhe ne ngu ya cwu miimi, a he ne mbe he, “Nyi ku Be̱ne̱ kishi nyi ri kpe a mwa ri.”
A he, “ꞌBe̱, kundu ngwe̱ shî, ning fo kwrreshi cinci ne̱. Gbengbe ni, ko nyi kya ce̱ nje we̱, se we na ngwe̱ re ci.”
Ya njeli i wru zinye̱ be ya ne̱ ne ki bra igbe̱.
Aha ne ngu shi cinci we yang, aa ning bra ku Be̱ne̱ we yang, he̱rri aa krro ci we yang, ci nna kpi be shi shi nyi roshwo.
A zhe ne ngu deze nwie ku Be̱ne̱, aa ning brru re nzhi nwie nné ki zhwe ngu. Aa ya we she ne mbe shi ndzie aha ne mbe rwe̱ ne rehwie dzio.
Wire ngu a he ne mbe he, “Nyi nda ngu ci ne nyi shi ndzie e̱e̱? Nyi deze nyi ku Be̱ne̱ kishi nyi ri kpe a zhe ne mwa ri ngu be.”
Á pie Jesu<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.47-56">Mat 26:47-56</a>; <a href="b41.14.43-50">Mar 14:43-50</a>; <a href="b43.18.2-11">Yoh 18:2-11</a>)We ne ngu shi we nka, brra ekpri nneywí ya wre̱ ngbe ya a tsi nné ki zhwe shwa ne otu wehwie ne e ki ye he Yahuda, ne ngu we kwa yi ncwuee. Aa be nwie Jesu, aa ki dzie ne me ushwo.
Me̱di Jesu he ne ngu he, “Yahuda, ngwe̱ shi rie̱ Kowe Nneywi e̱ ne me ushwo aa?”
Re̱se̱ ne kpi nné ki zhwe ngu a á zrre̱ ni, mbe e̱ he ne ngu he, “Brrabe̱, nzhi kwe̱ ne re-ise̱nkeli nzhi ne̱ e̱e̱?”
Ya mbe fie̱ ce e ning tsa uucwu nva nyye ꞌhwie Brra Prristi he̱rri aa ki kpo uucwu nna.
Me̱di Jesu he, “We ni! Aa be ni!” Wire Jesu re uucwu nne nna, aa ki kyia.
Jesu a he ne nggwé̱ re-prristi ngbe nnencwueé nné cwo Brranyi ngbe brrá nné ne mbe be ki pie he, “Nje nyi nne nca aa, ne nyi be ning pie ne re-ise̱nkeli ngbe ne ngbó ni e̱e̱?
Nje shi ngbe ne nyi a Brranyi ko zohu otu, ko nyi ree na va he nyi ning pie we̱. Me̱di nke e̱ nyi zhe nyi, zhe ne rewienci mbe shi ning ye ringgwe̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b42.19.47">Luk 19:47</a>; <a href="b42.21.37">21:37</a>
Pita klo he ko ngu hu Jesu we̱<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.57-58">Mat 26:57-58</a>, <a href="b40.26.69-75">69-75</a>; <a href="b41.14.53-54">Mar 14:53-54</a>, <a href="b41.14.66-72">66-72</a>; <a href="b43.18.12-18">Yoh 18:12-18</a>, <a href="b43.18.25-27">25-27</a>)Wire á pie Jesu, á ne̱ ne ngu re nzhi mi a ri Brra Prristi, me̱di Pita we zhwe ze̱nze̱.
A zhe ne mbe yhwa ro mbe shi wing a tese ri nna, Pita ya ne̱ ne wing ngbe ne mbe.
Ya ewena ne ngu nyi cwuo a ri nna a di Pita we gbinnng a zhe ne ngu shi srra dudu ne ro nna ngu a he, “Nne ne̱ i shi ngbe Jesu ma!”
Me̱di Pita klo nwie he, “Kei ewena ne! Ko nje ki hu we̱!”
Á srra we tsie̱, ya nne ki ri ngu a he ne ngu he, “Cence, ngwe̱ nyi ya mbe!”Me̱di Pita ki shing he, “Kei rwe! Ko nyi nje we̱.”
Á srra á ci awa zunzrru, ya mbe ngu a he wa he, “Nyi cence, nne ne̱ i shi ngbe Jesu, aha a nyi nne Galili.”
Me̱di Pita he, “Ka, a rwe! Ko nje hu ngbe kya ne ngwe̱ he ne̱ we̱!” We ne ko ngu ku onu we̱, ꞌgba wre̱ ne tsie̱.
Wire Brrabe̱ bra di Pita, Pita ngu a lu ne kya ne Brrabe̱ he ne ngu he, “Koó ri ma ne ꞌgba tsie̱ a totu cwu ne̱ we̱, ngwe̱ ri klo he ko ngwe̱ ning hu we̱ ce ꞌtsie̱.”
Wire Pita a wru ci i ya ku we ku we ku.
