Pita klo he ko ngu hu Jesu we̱<TS3>(<a href="b40.26.69-70">Mat 26:69-70</a>; <a href="b41.14.66-68">Mar 14:66-68</a>; <a href="b42.22.55-57">Luk 22:55-57</a>)Sima Pita ngbe yaka nne zhwe Jesu wa á zhwe Jesu. Ngu nne nke ana a zhwe Jesu re nzhi wre̱ he̱rri tese ri Brra Prristi nna, aha Brra Prristi e̱ ki hu.
