“Aha nii, a ri nje, koo mwa ye̱ye̱rri nzhi ci Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ ne mbe shi nwie klu re be nwie Be̱ne̱ re we bi rwe̱ we̱.
Me̱di nzhi we wie krre̱de̱ he de̱ ré ye yâ na ne e ngwá kpanshwu we̱, aha ko shi wiri a nyyi Be̱ne̱ we̱, ré we ni e̱ngwie̱ njè, ré we ni ye rine̱ kya ne e ki ci cwue ci ci, ré we ni ye roshwo.<RF q=+><a href="b2.34.15-17">Wru 34:15-17</a>; <a href="b3.17.10-16">Liv 17:10-16</a>; <a href="b3.18.6-23">18:6-23</a>
Aha á nyi ne hwie krre̱de̱ Nti Nka Musa a tu we gbangba a re-zonggrung mwe a ko zohu Kotung Srra Cwu, á bra brro nka nna a ko zohu ngwie̱.”
Krre̱de̱ re nzhi nwie Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ ne mbe si ywe̱Wire nnenté, ngbe brrá nné ngbe ekpri nné ce̱ nka zhwozhwo mbe e̱ shî he aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri mbe trru yá nné a tsi ekpri na mbe, mbe we te re nzhi Antakyia ngbe Bulu ngbe Barrnaba. Mbe e̱ kyie Yahuda ne e ki ye Barrsaba ngbe Sila ne mbe shi tsi nnencwueé nné ce̱ nka.
