Bulu ngbe Barrnaba á a hwie̱ srra we Antakyia a miimi nwie mie̱ nka ré brro Nka Rina Brrabe̱ ngbe yá nné piriri.
Bulu ngbe Barrnaba a ci kankaYa ꞌzhe he ngu a grra, Bulu a he ne Barrnaba he, “Ning be nzhi ya grra a ga re-ngwie̱ ne nzhi ning brro nka Brrabe̱ ngbe nzhi dzie re-gimbe nzhi ri ka á shi nyi rimi ye̱.”
Barrnaba a ce̱ fo Yohana ne e ki ye he Marrku re we zhwe.
Me̱di Bulu a hwie he ko shi re shi ye̱ye̱rri mbe ki fo we̱ aha Yohana i to we we a ngwie̱ Pamfiliya, ko i ce̱ ywa ncwuo ngbe mbe we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b44.13.13">RNné 13:13</a>
