A nyi ngu ꞌjee ne̱ ne ga re-nkla nzhi shwa ne otu wehwie zhwozhwo mbe ning sa riyii he mbe ri ngu ci rrurru, kya a nyi ngwiee mbe srra re ye Be̱ne̱ mbè totu ne te̱ne̱. A bra nyi we aha kya ne nzhi ning sa riyii ne̱, Brra Be̱ri, ne mbe nné Yahudi ne̱ mbe bra bi nka a rici nje!
Nyi nda ngu ci ne nyi e̱ nyi ra shing he Be̱ne̱ hung deze nné kwi e̱ ye̱?
“Nje ne̱ we rici nje ma, nje i fo he ka shi ye̱ye̱rri, nje nyi ko nda ne nje hung nying nwie ce̱trri lo Jesu nne Nazarra ne̱.<RF q=+><a href="b44.8.3">RNné 8:3</a>; <a href="b44.22.4-5">22:4-5</a>
Kya ne nje i srra re nying a Urrushelima a nyi ngwiee ana. Nggwé̱ re-prristi e̱ i ning ngwa de̱me̱ ne nje prre nné Be̱ne̱ piriri re we ci uucwu gyiaa. He̱rri kundu ne e we yhwi, ma n yo re shing he shi ye̱ye̱rri.
He̱rri a re-zhe piriri, nje i we ngwa cinci a re-zonggrung mwe nwie we nyie̱ ne ce ré he nkang dzie̱ lo Jesu. Aha ehwie shwo nje ne mbe, he̱rri nje i cwo re-ngwie̱ ne mbe shi gbong we aha n ya we ngwa ge̱zhe̱.
Bulu ti rê ne ngu ning bra ngu hwie̱ nne ce̱ nka<TS3>(<a href="b44.9.1-19">RNné 9:1-19</a>; <a href="b44.22.6-16">22:6-16</a>)“A nyi aha ni ne nje i nyia re nzhi Damaska ne nggwé̱ re-prristi mbe ning ngwa de̱me̱ ngbe re-krre̱de̱ igbe̱ng nyi cwuo nna.
Brra Be̱ri, a i nyi we brra tsi te̱ne̱ ne nje shi rê, nje e̱ ri nse̱ ngu tsie̱ ke̱sss, a si re ne̱ ꞌne̱, nse̱ nna a wru zinye̱ ngu a si re ning grra ngbe nné ne mbe shi ciee ngbe nje.
Ga nzhi zhwozhwo nzhi kpi be, ngbe nje e̱ ho ya cwue ngu he nka ne nje a zhe Ibrrani he, ‘Shawulu, Shawulu! Aha nda ngwe̱ ning ngwá ge̱zhe̱ ni e̱? Ngwe̱ shi nwie yaa ngwa cinci we rici ngwe̱ shi shi izhimi ne ngu ci ta re ning le ekwe rre̱rre̱ nne ki cwo.’
“Nje e̱ ki rinng he, ‘Nyi ngwe̱ nye̱ e̱, Brrabe̱?’“Brrabe̱ ngu a shî he, ‘Nyi nje Jesu ngwe̱ shi ning ngwa ge̱zhe̱ ne̱.
Me̱di deze ngwe̱ yo yo ne nta ngwe̱. Nje be nwie ngwe̱ ne̱ aha ngbe n re ci ngwe̱ hwie̱ nnencwuo nje ngbe sheede nje a ko nda ne ngwe̱ ri a nje ngbe re-ankya ne nje shi re ting.
Nje shi re kye̱ ne nné ngwe̱, nné Isrreela, ngbe Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ ne nje re te nwie mbe.
Ngwe̱ shi we kla nyyi, ngwe̱ we klu a nwie ywing re be nwie si, ngwe̱ we trru a nva igbe̱ Shetani re be nwie Be̱ne̱, ngbe aha sa rie mbe a nje, ma n we we re-e̱ngwie̱ mbe, ngbe wé̱ she ewie a nwie nné ne Be̱ne̱ e̱ we ci ré hwie̱ nné ngu.’
Bulu ti zhwe cwuo ngu“Aha nii, Nggwe̱ Agrripa, ko nje ra shî nka ne Be̱ne̱ ngu ning ting a yarri revi e̱ we̱.
Nje ce̱ ce̱ucwung a Damaska re nzhi Urrushelima ngbe ga re-nkla ngwie̱ Yahudi zhwozhwo he̱rri re nzhi nwie Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ ma. Nje we brrong he ré si ywe̱ ré bra re be nwie Be̱ne̱, ré bra nyi re-ankya na mbe ti he mbe si ywe̱.<RF q=+><a href="b44.9.20">RNné 9:20</a>, <a href="b44.9.28-29">28-29</a>
