Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ he, “Ko nye̱ ne ngu sa rie a ngu, ko shi re shwe nshwu we̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b23.28.16 (LXX)">Ish 28:16 (LXX)</a>
Mahu a hé a rici ko nye̱. Ko bi nka he nne nke nyi nné Yahudi, nke ncwi e̱ nyi Nne Nzhwe Ngwie̱ we̱. A nyi we Brrabe̱ zunzrru ne ngu nyi Brrabe̱ na ga nné zhwozhwo. Ga nné ne mbe ki kyie̱ e̱ zhwozhwo, a we mwo rina piriri.
Aha Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ he, “Ko nye̱ ne ngu kyie̱ Brrabe̱ e̱ we̱ she kyia.”<RF q=+><a href="b29.2.32">Yow 2:32</a>
Ma wé̱ ce̱ rimi ré kyie̱ nne ne ko mbe sa rie a ngu we̱ e̱ ye̱? Wé̱ ce̱ rimi ré sa rie a ngu ne ko mbe ho nka ngu we̱ e̱ ye̱? Ka wé̱ ce̱ rimi ré ho ne ko ya nne e we brro nka we̱ e̱ ye̱?
Ka wé̱ bra ce̱ rimi ya nne re we brro nka we̱sa ne e ki te e̱ ye̱? A shi we shi ne e wie he, “Kundu ne nné brro Nka Rina mbe e ya wre̱, a nyi kya rina kpe̱kpe̱!”<RF q=+><a href="b23.52.7">Ish 52:7</a>
Me̱di ko nyi ga nné Isrreela zhwozhwo ne mbe se̱ Nka Rina nna we̱. Ishaya i he he, “Brrabe̱, nyi nye̱ ngu shî nka nzhi e̱?”<RF q=+><a href="b23.53.1 (LXX)">Ish 53:1 (LXX)</a>
Aha ni ga nné ne mbe sa rie e̱ á sa rie aha ne mbe ho nka ne e we brrong, nka ne e we brrong nna nyi nka Krristi.
Me̱di nje rin he: Nyi cence he ko á i ho we̱ e̱e̱? Á i ho shi. Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.19.4 (LXX)">Rve 19:4 (LXX)</a>“Nka mbe e̱ se̱ ngwie̱ yu zhwozhwo,he̱rri nka mbe e̱ ya cwu krruci ngwie̱.”
Nje bra rin te̱nte̱ wa: Ko nné Isrreela i hu re̱se̱ng we̱ e̱e̱? Musa i ke̱she shî Be̱ne̱ng he,“Nje ri ci rehwie mbe ré yhwiaha nné mbe ne ko mbe nyi nné nje we̱;rehwie mbe ri ye gbushwoaha nné re-ngwie̱ riywe̱ zentsi.”
Ishaya i he we gbeng he,<RF q=+><a href="b23.65.1 (LXX)">Ish 65:1 (LXX)</a>“Nné ne ko mbe ning kre we̱, á ning she;Nné ne ko mbe rin aha nje we̱, nje we ti rici nje.”
Me̱di Be̱ne̱ he nka a rici nné Isrreela he, “Nje yerí yeri nwie nyie̱ va he n se̱ nné nje ne mbe ra ning ho nka ne mbe bra ning klo rici.”<RF q=+><a href="b23.65.2 (LXX)">Ish 65:2 (LXX)</a>
Be̱ne̱ e̱ ri naana nné IsrreelaAha ni nje rin he: Ma Be̱ne̱ e̱ ra nne ngu aa? Aawo, ko tsie̱nzhwu! Nje we rici nje e̱ nje nyi nne Isrreela, a nzhwe Ibrrahin, nje wru a nkla Benjemi.<RF q=+><a href="b50.3.5">Fil 3:5</a>
Ko Be̱ne̱ ra nné ngu ne ngu i ke̱nce̱ we kyie we̱. Ko nyi hu kya ne Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ he ne Iliya a zhe ne ngu i cwe nva ne Be̱ne̱ a rici nné Isrreela we̱ e̱e̱? A i he,
“Brrabe̱, á yhwi nné ti re̱se̱ng ngwe̱, á gywi re-briing nyi teede ngwe̱. A nyi we nje nggaa nje ne nje hwie̱, á bra shi kre rê ré ning yhwe̱ ma?”<RF q=+><a href="b11.19.10">1Ngg 19:10</a>, <a href="b11.19.14">14</a>
Be̱ne̱ i ki shing he rimi? A i he, “A bi nné ꞌci natsie̱ ne nje yaa sang ne ko mbe sa hu be ngbe ré ye kpanshwu ne e ki ye he Baali e̱ mbè we̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b11.19.18">1Ngg 19:18</a>
A shi we ni a zhe ne ne̱ wa: a bi kpi mbe tsie̱ ne Be̱ne̱ ngu kyie ngu we aha ehwie rina ngu.
Ma shi rimi rri ii? Kya ne nné Isrreela mbe i ning tu rici nwie kreng ne ko mbe she we̱, nyi ngwiee ne nné na ne Be̱ne̱ ngu kyie mbe she. Kpi mbe hwie̱ we nné klo nci.
A shi we shi ne e wie he,<RF q=+><a href="b5.29.4">NNMN 29:4</a>; <a href="b23.29.10">Ish 29:10</a>“Be̱ne̱ e̱ ci rehwie mbe ci we̱e̱ ywing ne riywe̱ hung,á bi nyyi me̱di koó ri ewie we̱,á bi re-uucwu, me̱di koó ho nka we̱,he̱rri re be wre̱ cwu.”
Dooda i bra he wa he,“Nde rewie para mbe ré we hwie̱ etsie;ré we hwie̱ ankyang grre̱.Nde ré we hwie̱ rewie ne mbe shi ning shwe cinci!
Nde nyyi mbe ré ci ywing he̱rri ré me̱nkye̱ng ri ewie;ngbe re-teme mbe ré gwe he̱rri tiya aha ge̱zhe̱.”
Nje bra rin wa he, Nné Isrreela i grre̱ kpi we kprrenkprrenkprre he̱rri ko bi na ré bra cinye̱ wa wo ye̱? Aawo, ko tsie̱nzhwu! E̱ngwie̱ mbe e̱ ci kyia be nwie Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ aha ngbe re ci rehwie nné Isrreela ré yhwi.
Ma kundu e̱ngwie̱ mbe e̱ ngwa ebe ngwie̱ mwo rina, ne ywe̱ mbe e̱ ci Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ shwe rishwe ni, ma kundu ga nné Yahudi ne e kyie e̱ mbe ri she ngwie ngbe re-mwo rina nna wé̱ ngra brri we brri rimi!
Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ e̱ á she kyiaNje shi nka a zhe ne ne̱ ne nyi Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱, tu ne nje nyi nnente re be nwie Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱. Nje ning cwé zewe ne cwuo nje ne̱,
he ka de̱e̱nte̱ wo, n ci rehwie nné na nje e̱ ré yhwi, he ngbe n ci yá mbe ré she kyia.
Aha a zhe ne i we ra, ngbe nné be ngwie̱ zhwozhwo a she riwie̱ng she srra shwe̱ ngbe Be̱ne̱. Ma rinang nna ri ngra shi rimi a zhe ne Be̱ne̱ ri we se̱ e̱? We̱ shi shi nné kwi ne e we deze nce!
Ma nzhi ning mwa yi ne nda? Tu ne cwe yâ nke ne e vie ngwa Be̱ne̱ e̱ shi wiri, mahu re̱se̱ kya ngu hwie̱ e̱ shi wiri ma. Kundu ne riti ekwe e̱ shi wiri, mahu ga re-nva nna zhwozhwo wé̱ shi wiri ma.
Mbe nné Yahudi e̱ á shi shi yá nva ekwe rihwie̱n na ne e kye̱ ne e bra kprre nva nna á wa, wire á a nyi mi ne nyi ne nyi shi shi nva rekwe na rihwie̱n yi, á a ya ning rwe nyrra mi. A zhe ne ne̱ nyi e̱ shi nwie ho shwi rishi ruto na te̱nte̱ ekwe rihwie̱n nke ne e kye̱ e̱ ne ngu kwa ne re-rinyie ngu.
Aha ni shi de̱ ngwe̱ we dzie̱ mbe ne mbe shi shi nva ekwe nke ne e kprre wa a we̱. Shi de̱ ngwe̱ cwe zewe we̱. Ngwe̱ nyi we vang, ko nyi ngwe̱ ne ngwe̱ bro riti ekwe nna we̱, a nyi riting nna ngu re bro ngwe̱ e̱.
Me̱di ngwe̱ bra hung he he, “Ee, nje he ka á i kprre nva ekwe nna aha ngbe nje e̱ n she ngwie ye̱ e̱e̱.”
A shi ni cence. Á i we kprre mbe e̱ á wa aha riywe̱ sa rie mbe, ngbe ngwe̱ e̱ she ngwie aha sa rie ngwe̱. Me̱di shi de̱ ngwe̱ bra ne̱ ne kywo rici ze we̱, yo ne owu.
Kundu ne ko Be̱ne̱ i we nné Yahudi ne mbe shi shi te̱nte̱ nva rekwe we̱, ngwe̱ hwie he we̱ re we ngwe̱ e̱e̱?
Aha ni ri zhwe ehwie rina Be̱ne̱ ngbe ren ngu ne̱. Aa ngwa nné mbe ne mbe ra sa rie a ngu cinci, ngu a re nyi ngwe̱ e̱ rina, me̱di se ne ngwe̱ ke̱ we ne yo we yarri ehwie rina ngu wire. De̱e̱ ni we̱, wé̱ re tsa wé̱ zhwu ma.
Kundu mbe nné Yahudi e̱ mbe ning brru sa rie a ngu, we̱ ning brru ne mbe re be riting nna, aha Be̱ne̱ e̱ hu ning brru ne mbe te̱nte̱ wa.
Ma he̱rri kundu ngwe̱ ne ngwe̱ shi shi ngwe̱ nyi va ekwe rihwie̱n yi ne Be̱ne̱ i re fo bia a te̱nte̱ ekwe rihwie̱n, ne ngu bi rwe̱ ré nyi ni e̱, we̱ ce̱ rimi re me̱nkye̱ ning brru mi ne nva rekwe na te̱nte̱ ekwe rihwie̱n nna aa?
Be̱ne̱ ri naana ko nye̱Re-gimbe, ko nje ce̱ nyi nyi riywe̱ hu nka ne ngu shi la la ne̱ we̱, kishi nyi ri ne̱ ne yaa kywo he nyi bi zentsi. Kpi nné Isrreela a á ci gbanggrraa aha se ne rigbre Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ nke ne mbe shi ngwie nwie Be̱ne̱ e̱ ri ya cwu ye̱ye̱rri wire.
Wire ga nné Isrreela zhwozhwo ri she kyia, shi ne Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ he:<RF q=+><a href="b23.59.20 (LXX)">Ish 59:20 (LXX)</a>“Nnenkyia a ri wru a Siyonangbe we̱ yi ga re-ngwie̱ngwie̱ nzhwe Yakubu.
ꞌJee nje ngbe mbe e̱ nyi nke:<RF q=+><a href="b24.31.33-34">Iri 31:33-34</a>á ri he zhe ana nje ri we we re-e̱ngwie̱ mbe.”
Aha ne nné Yahudi e̱ mbe ra Nka Rina ne̱, á hwie̱ rwinkó Be̱ne̱, aa a bra hwie̱ rinang a nwie nyi, nyi Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱. Me̱di a nka kyie ne Be̱ne̱ ngu i we kyie, a we cé̱ aha brrá re-yo mbe na tiya.
Aha kya na na Be̱ne̱ re be nwie mbe ngbe ye ne ngu we ye e̱, ko shi re bra we we̱.
Aha we shi nyi Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ e̱ nyi i ra ho Be̱ne̱ nka gbangba tiya a, a zhe ne ne̱ a rí naana nyi aha riywe̱ ho nka nné Yahudi.
A shi we ni wa, shi ne nyi i ra ho Be̱ne̱ nka, ngu a ri naana nyi, nné Yahudi e̱ á ra ki ho nka, ngbe Be̱ne̱ we̱ ri naana mbe shi ne ngu ri naana nyi ma.
Be̱ne̱ e̱ ci ga nneywí zhwozhwo á hwie̱ shi nné gyiaa aha riywe̱ ho nka, aha ngbe ngu ri naana ko nye̱ mbe.
De Brrabe̱Ehwie rina Be̱ne̱ e̱ zhwo we zhwo!Zentsi ngu a shi cwuncwuncwuu!Hu re̱se̱ng na ngu a ko bi krrucing we̱!<RF q=+><a href="b23.55.8">Ish 55:8</a>Nyi nye̱ re hung hu re-kyankya ne ngu rwe e̱e̱?Nyi nye̱ re hung hu nhwie̱ ngu aa?
“Nyi nye̱ ngu sa hu kya ne ngu shi nu rie Brrabe̱ e̱?<RF q=+><a href="b23.40.13 (LXX)">Ish 40:13 (LXX)</a>Nyi nye̱ re hung ki sheng ne nka aa?
Nyi nye̱ ngu sa ki ngwa yankya,<RF q=+><a href="b18.41.11">Ayu 41:11</a>he̱rri ngbe ré he re trra aa?”
Zhwe srra na ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri nzhi hu ning nyi Be̱ne̱ cwuoAha nii, re-gimbe, nje cwe nva ne nyi aha Be̱ne̱ e̱ ri naana nzhi we yang, he nyi ngwa nci nyi shi nyi kyang nyi teede nke ne ngu shi nce, ne ngu shi wiri ngu bra klá Be̱ne̱ ehwie. Nyi ngwiee ngu nyi te̱nte̱ ye mbè ne nyi ye Be̱ne̱ng.
Shi de̱ nyi fo e̱kpe̱e̱ nné riywe̱ hu Be̱ne̱ a nze̱ ne̱ we̱, me̱di nde Be̱ne̱ re níng bra ngbe nyi ci hwihwíng a yarri rehwie nyi. Wire nyi e̱ hung hu ka nyi nda ngu nyi kya ce̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱, ne ngu nyi kya te̱nte̱ng, kya ne ngu ki kla ehwie, ne ngu shi tsantsa a nyyi ngu.
Aha ehwie rina Be̱ne̱ re be nwie nje, nje he ne ko nye̱ a tsi nyi he: shi de̱ ya nyi re yaa fo shi ngu wara kya ne ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri ne ngu we̱. Me̱di ko nye̱ re nywe̱ rici a yarri hwie nka ngu, re ri rici ngu we ye̱ye̱rri ne ewie Be̱ne̱ ngu ki sa a yarri ce̱ nka.
A shi we shi ne ko nye̱ nzhi bi rekpri rwe̱ piriri a rwe̱ ngu, ko rekpri rwe̱ nna zhwozhwo nyi we zhwe cwuo zunzrru we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b46.12.12">1Kor 12:12</a>
Aha ni a yarri Krristi e̱ nzhi brri we brri, me̱di nzhi shi zunzrru, ko zohu ekpri rwe̱ nna a mwe ngbe ya.
Aha ni nzhi bi re-beewa kanka kanka ye̱ye̱rri ne kya Be̱ne̱ ngu níng ngwa a yarri ehwie rina ngu. Kundu ya ri bi beewang ti re̱se̱ng, we̱ ti re̱se̱ng ye̱ye̱rri ne sa rie ngu.<RF q=+><a href="b46.12.4-11">1Kor 12:4-11</a>
A ri nyi nang nyi cwuong she nnéng, we̱ nyi cwuong she nnéng; a ri nyi nang mie̱ nka, we̱ mie̱ nka;
a ri nyi nang shwe̱ nneywí rehwie, we̱ shwe̱ nneywí rehwie; a ri nyi nang ngwang aha ré she nnéng, we̱ ngwa ne ehwie zunzrru; a ri nyi nang kwa nneywí yincwuee, we̱ ning tu rici kwa yincwuee e̱ rina rina; a ri nyi nang she ꞌyiriywé̱ng a yarri naana, we̱ we sheng ne ehwie kla.
Ce̱Nde ce̱ ne nyi yaa ce̱ e̱ re nyi cence. Nyi ce̱trri kya ne ngu shi ngwie̱ngwie̱, nyi bro we kya ne ngu nyi te̱nte̱ng.
We shi re-gimbe, nyi yaa ce̱ gbagba. Ngwa nné grime̱ shi á re ne̱.
Shi de̱ nyi we we̱sa ning tu rici ncwuo we̱, nde rehwie nyi ré yhwi aha cwuo Be̱ne̱.
Nde nyi bi rehwie kla aha kya ne nyi ning sa riyii, nyi bi rehwie sheng a yarri re-cinci nyi, nyi ke̱ we ne ku Be̱ne̱ ko zohu zhe.
Nyi ri ma kye kya ne nyi bi e̱ ngbe nyi na nné ce̱ nka nke ne ko mbe bi we̱, nyi se̱ nné ice ne nva wehwie.
Nyi mwo nné ne mbe níng ngwa cinci rina. We mwo rina, shi de̱ nyi mwo he ré ngwie ge̱zhe̱ we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.5.44">Mat 5:44</a>; <a href="b42.6.28">Luk 6:28</a>
Nyi nyi rekwi ngbe nné ne mbe shi rekwi, nyi bra ku rana ngbe nné ne mbe shi rana.
Nyi srra rina ngbe ko nye̱. Shi de̱ nyi yaa kywo we̱, me̱di nyi shî ngbe nyi mwe rici ngbe nné mbe ne mbe re̱. Shi de̱ nyi hwie he nyi ne̱ nné e̱ ne zentsi we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b20.3.7">NNZh 3:7</a>
Shi de̱ nyi trra e̱ngwie̱ ne e̱ngwie̱ we̱. Nyi ci nkwile̱ ngbe nyi nyi kya ne ngu shi ye̱ye̱rri a nwie ko nye̱.
Nyi nyi ko nda ne nyi ri hung nying aha ngbe nyi srra rina ngbe ko nye̱.
Nné ce̱ nje, shi de̱ nyi trra e̱ngwie̱ we̱, me̱di nyi we Be̱ne̱ re níng trrang ne ren ngu. Aha á wie he: “Trrang nyi ngge nje, nje ri trra, kya ne Brrabe̱ e̱ he e̱ nyi ngwiee.”<RF q=+><a href="b5.32.35">NNMN 32:35</a>
Me̱di shi kya ne Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ he,“Kundu rwinko ngwe̱ shi ne nzhwo,ki ngwa yâ ye.Kundu ꞌne̱ rishi ki hwe,ki ngwa rishi shwe.Kundu ngwe̱ nyi ni, ngwe̱ e̱ ki ci nshwu<RF q=+>ngwe̱ e̱ ki ci nshwu:Krre̱de̱ na nka Heleni he he,“ngwe̱ e̱ ki kro ro rice̱ a rici”.”<RF q=+><a href="b20.25.21-22 (LXX)">NNZh 25:21-22 (LXX)</a>
Shi de̱ ngwe̱ we e̱ngwie̱ re shwe igbe̱ ngwe̱ we̱, me̱di nyi shwe igbe̱ e̱ngwie̱ ne re-cwuo rina.
Ngwa ringgwe̱ ngwie̱ grime̱Se ko nye̱ re ngwa ringgwe̱ ngwie̱ grime̱, aha ko bi ya ringgwe̱ ne ngu nyi Be̱ne̱ ngu we̱sa cing we̱. Ga re-ringgwe̱ ne nzhi bi ne̱ nyi Be̱ne̱ ngu ci.
Aha ni ko nye̱ ne ngu ra ho nka ringgwe̱, mahu a ce̱trri kya ne Be̱ne̱ ngu rwe sa; ko nye̱ ne ngu bra nyi ni e̱ shi yaa be mi ne nyi nka a rici ngu.
Ko nnencwueé e̱ á nyi kya owu a nwie nné nyi kya ne ngu shi ye̱ye̱rri we̱. Ngwe̱ cé̱ srra we dengge we̱sa ne owu nné ringgwe̱ e̱e̱? Ma nyi kya ne ngu shi ye̱ye̱rri, ngbe wé̱ re de.
Aha á nyi nnencwuó Be̱ne̱ ngbe ré re nyi ngwe̱ e̱ rinang. Me̱di kundu ngwe̱ ywe̱, ci owu mbe, aha koó bro re-ise̱nkeli mbe e̱ we shweni we̱. Aha á nyi nnencwuó Be̱ne̱ aha ngbe ré ngwa nné bi vini cinci shi kya Be̱ne̱ cé̱.
Aha ni, aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri nyi ho nka ringgwe̱ ngwie̱ e̱, ko we aha ne nyi to shwe cinci we̱, me̱di aha de̱ nyi bi vini a yarri ronu rie nyi we̱.
Kya a nyi ngwiee ne nyi trra gondu a, aha nnencwuo gonati e̱ á nyi nnencwuó Be̱ne̱, ne mbe ngwa zhe mbe zhwozhwo aha cwuo ringgwe̱ ngwie̱.<RF q=+><a href="b40.22.21">Mat 22:21</a>; <a href="b41.12.17">Mar 12:17</a>; <a href="b42.20.25">Luk 20:25</a>
Aha ni nyi trra ko nye̱ kya ne ngu níng zhwe: nne nke ne ngu si gondu, ki trrang; nne nke ne ngu si ncwe̱ng ankya, ki trrang; nne nke ne ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri ngwe̱ to owu ngu, to owu ngu, nne nke ne ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri ngwe̱ ki ngwa grime̱, ki ngwa.
Nzhi yaa ce̱ a nci nzhiShi de̱ nyi bro tsie ya nne we̱sa trrang we̱; se ka tsie nke ne e zhwe ko nye̱, nyi ngwiee ngu nyi he nyi yaa ce̱. Ko nye̱ ne ngu nyí nke ne̱ mahu a zhwé Nti Nka ye̱ye̱rri.
Ko ce̱ e̱ nyi nke he ngwe̱ nyi nne dudu ne ngwe̱ ꞌhwie̱ we̱. Mahu kundu ngwe̱ ce̱ nne dudu ne ngwe̱ e̱, ngwe̱ e̱ zhwe Nti Nka zhwozhwo.
Kotu a sa duduAha ni, se nyi nyi ni, aha nyi hu zhwe zhe ne nzhi ning shi ne̱. Zhe e̱ be ngbe nyi shwo ndzie. Zhe ne e shi níng kyia a sa dudu re ne̱ zhe ne nzhi i ning si ywe̱.
Totu a nyia, mincwe e̱ ri kpa kla. Aha ni nzhi we ni re-cwuo na ewie ywing ngbe nzhi hwrra ankyang ko na ewie si.
Nde nzhi srra zhwe srra te̱nte̱ng shi nné ne mbe srra a nwie si brra te̱ne̱ — ko a re-parang shwe ankyang dzio nci we̱, ka shwe ankyang ci zhing we̱, ka le̱le̱ njè we̱, ka nyi ankya nshwu we̱, ka yaa ti ka we̱, ka ci riyii a ankya nné we̱.
Me̱di nyi yaa sha ne e̱kpe̱e̱ Brrabe̱ Jesu Krristi. Shi de̱ nyi hwie nkang ho shwi ankya ecwue na ikpe rwe̱ we̱.
Shi de̱ ngwe̱ nyi ya nne nka we̱Nne nke ne sa rie ngu a shi brrubrru, nyi ki se̱; shi de̱ nyi ki ti onu ce nwie he e brru aha kya ne ngu ning hwie yi e̱ shi ka ne na nyi we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b51.2.16">Kol 2:16</a>
Yá mbe bi sa rie he mbe e̱ hung ye ko nda ne mbe ce̱, me̱di ya ne sa rie ngu a shi brrubrru we̱ ce̱ ye we ankya mbe ne e tsi a nhwie̱n.
Shi de̱ nne nke ne ngu hung ye ko nda re dzie̱ nne ne ngu ra ye kpi re-ankya we̱; shi de̱ nne nke ne ngu yé we kya ne e tsi tsi a nhwie̱n ma re dzie̱ nne ne ngu yé ko nda we̱, aha ga mbe zhwozhwo Be̱ne̱ we ce̱.
Nyi ngwe̱ nye̱ ngwe̱ nyi ꞌhwie yaka ya nne nka aa? A nyi we be̱ri ngu a ngu hung he aa nyi ye̱ye̱rri ka aa ywe̱. Aha nyi Brrabe̱ ngu hung ki ci re yo tsantsa.
Ya nne e̱ fo ya otu a ki ne̱ kpi rotu a zhwozhwo, ya a ri ga rotu a zhwozhwo ki nyi we zunzrru. Nde ko nye̱ re fo kya ne ngu hu he shi tsantsa a yarri hwie ngu.
Nne nke ne ngu fo he ya otu ki ne̱ kpi rotu a, aa ki fo ni aha grime̱ Brrabe̱. Nne nke ne ngu bra yé ko nda a wa, a nyi ni aha grime̱ Brrabe̱, aha a cí Be̱ne̱ kijie̱ng. Nne nke ma ne ngu rá ye yá re-ankya, a nyi ni aha grime̱ Be̱ne̱, aha ngu a ma a cí Be̱ne̱ kijie̱ng.
Ko bi ya nzhi ne ngu srra we aha rici ngu we̱; ko bra bi nne ngu shi hu we aha rici ngu wa we̱.
Kundu nzhi shi nce, we̱ nyi we aha grime̱ Brrabe̱ ne nzhi shi nce; kundu ne nzhi bra kwi, nzhi e̱ kwi we aha grime̱ Brrabe̱. Aha ni ka nzhi shi nce ka nzhi kwi, nzhi nyi we na Brrabe̱.
A nyi aha ni ne Krristi i hu, ngu bra ning brru deze nce, aha ngu hwie̱ Brrabe̱ na nné nce ngbe nné kwi.
Ma aha nda ne ngwe̱ e̱ ngwe̱ ri vini gimbe ngwe̱ e̱e̱? Ngwe̱ e̱ ma, aha ngwe̱ dzie̱ gimbe ngwe̱ e̱ ma aa? Ga nzhi zhwozhwo nzhi ri yo a nyyi Be̱ne̱ ngbe re níng nyi nka.<RF q=+><a href="b47.5.10">2Kor 5:10</a>
Aha á wie he,<RF q=+><a href="b23.45.23 (LXX)">Ish 45:23 (LXX)</a>“Nje Brrabe̱ bi ce e̱ nje he,ko nye̱ ri hu be ne re-ruhuu ngu a nyyi nje,ko nye̱ we̱ he we ne onu ngu he nje nyi Be̱ne̱.”
Mahu ko nye̱ nzhi ri yo re he kya ne ngu nyi a nyyi Be̱ne̱.
Shi de̱ ngwe̱ ci ya gimbe re grre̱ we̱Aha ni, nzhi we ni yaa nyie̱ nva re he nne nke ka nke bi vini. Ne re shi ni, canca ngwe̱ ngwe̱ fo a yarri ngwe̱ he ko shi ngwe̱ nyi yankya he̱rri re ci ya gimbe re grre̱ re kpe yarri e̱ngwie̱ we̱.
Nje hu cence he shi ni, aha nje shi yarri Brrabe̱ Jesu, nje hu he ko bi ko ya yâ ne ngu we̱sa shi wiri we̱; me̱di kundu ya hwié he ko ya yâ we̱sa shi wiri we̱, mahu ko shi wiri we̱ a nwie ngu.
Me̱di kundu aha kya ne ngwe̱ yé e̱ ngwe̱ shi ci ya gimbe re dzio ehwie, mahu kya ngwe̱ nyi e̱ tí he ko ngwe̱ ki ce̱ we̱. Shi de̱ kya ne ngwe̱ yé e̱ re hwie̱ kya ngu shi ci ya gimbe ne Krristi ngu hu aha ngu re ci shweni we̱.
Shi de̱ kya ne ngwe̱ hwie he bi rina a ré he he shi me̱nkye̱ we̱.
Aha ko Ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ nyi nkang ye re shwe we̱, me̱di nyi nka redziee, ngbe srra rina, ngbe ehwie kla ne Nshe Wiri ngu ngwa.
Kundu nneywí nyí Krristi cwuo ni, mahu wé̱ kla Be̱ne̱ ehwie, nneywí wé̱ bra he kya mbe nyi e̱ bi rina.
Aha ni, nde nzhi yaa rwe nwie nyi kya ne ngu shi be mi ne srra rina ngbe yaa ci cwo a nci nzhi.
Shi de̱ ngwe̱ dzio kya ne Be̱ne̱ ngu nyi aha kya ne ngwe̱ yé we̱. Ko bi ya yâ ne ngu we̱sa shi wiri we̱, me̱di a shi wie̱e̱ni ngbe ya nne re ye kya ne ngu shi ci ya re grre̱.
A nyi canca de̱ ngwe̱ ye ya rine̱, ka ngwe̱ shwe ya rishi ruto, ka ngwe̱ nyi yankya ne ngu shi ci ya gimbe re kpe yarri e̱ngwie̱ we̱.
Bro kya ne ngwe̱ ning hwie yi a nka ne̱ we hwie ngwe̱ ngbe Be̱ne̱. Mwo rina nyi na nne nke ne ko ngu ho a hwie ngu a he kya ne ngu nyi e̱ shi wie̱e̱ni we̱.
Me̱di nne nke ne ngu ki shi jinji a nka kya ne ngu ye e̱, mahu nyi Be̱ne̱ ngu ki ting he yeng nna shi wie̱e̱ni, aha kya ne ngu yé e̱ ko shi ye̱ye̱rri ne kya ngu ning sa rie we̱. Ko nda ne e nyi we̱sa ne sa rie e̱ nyi e̱ngwie̱.
Ci nneywí rehwie klaAa mwa ye̱ye̱rri nzhi ne sa rie nzhi e̱ bi igbe̱ nzhi she nné mbe ne sa rie mbe e̱ shi brrubrru ne re-brru mbe. Shi de̱ nzhi nyi we kya ne ngu shi ning ngwa nzhi e̱ ehwie kla we̱.
Aha ko ngbe Krristi e̱ ma ko i nyi yankya aha ngu yaa ngwa ehwie kla we rici ngu we̱. Me̱di a i ci we shi kya ne e wie he: “Ga re-cwi ne e re cwi ngwe̱ e̱ hwie̱ we rici nje.”<RF q=+><a href="b19.69.9">Rve 69:9</a>
Ko nda ne i wie a yarri Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ e̱ á i wie aha re níng mie̱ng, re bra níng shwe̱ rehwie aha ngbe nzhi hung yaa rwe nwie sa riyii a re-ankya ne Be̱ne̱ ngu níng sa ꞌjee.
Nde Be̱ne̱ ne ngu níng shwé̱ rehwie re níng sheng ngbe nyi hung yaa rwe aha nyi mwe rici a nci nyi nwie mie̱ zhwe srra na Krristi Jesu,
aha ngbe ga nyi zhwozhwo nyi ci onu ꞌzrru nwie de Be̱ne̱ ne ngu nyi ꞌBe̱ Brrabe̱ nzhi Jesu Krristi a yarri ronu rie nyi.
Nka Rina aha Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱Ko nye̱ ri ma si re-gimbe a yarri Krristi ne nva wehwie we shi ne Krristi ngu níng se̱ aha grime̱ Be̱ne̱ ma.
Nje níng ting he kya ngu i ci ne Krristi e̱ hwie̱ nnencwuo nné Yahudi e̱ nyi aha ngu ti raywrra Be̱ne̱, ngbe ngu bra ti he re-ꞌjee ne Be̱ne̱ ngu i sa brrá re-yo mbeng nna koo kpo we̱.
Aa bra i nyi ni aha ngbe Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ re de Be̱ne̱ aha naana ngu re be nwie mbe, shi ne e wie he,<RF q=+><a href="b10.22.50">2Sam 22:50</a>; <a href="b19.18.49">Rve 18:49</a>“Aha ni, nje shi re de a tsi Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱;Nje bra shi ce̱ re-veng de lo ngwe̱.”
Á bra wie wa he,<RF q=+><a href="b5.32.43">NNMN 32:43</a>“Nyi nyi rekwi,nyi Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱, ngbe nné na Be̱ne̱!”
A bra he wa he,“Nyi de Brrabe̱, ga nyi Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ zhwozhwo;nyi ki de, ga nyi nneywí zhwozhwo!”
Ishaya bra i he wa he,<RF q=+><a href="b23.11.10 (LXX)">Ish 11:10 (LXX)</a>“Ya ri wru a nzhwe Jese;ngbe we̱ ye ringgwe̱ a zete Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱,Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ e̱ wé̱ sa riyii a ngu.”
Nde Be̱ne̱ ne nzhi sa riyii a ngu re níng ngwa ehwie kla ngbe srra rina aha ne nyi sá rie a ngu, aha ngbe nyi ke̱ we ne ning bra sa riyii a ngu ne igbe̱ Nshe Wiri ne ngu níng sheng.
Kwili krre̱de̱ Bulu re nzhi nwie Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱Re-gimbe, nje we rici nje e̱ nje hu cence he nyi bi e̱kpe̱e̱ rina, nyi bra bi hu re̱se̱ nka Be̱ne̱ we yang, he nyi bra hung yaa mie̱ng we nci nyi.
Nje níng he yá re-nka a yarri krre̱de̱ ne̱ we dengge aha ne nje ce̱ níng lu te̱nte̱. A ning shi we dengge ni aha ehwie rina Be̱ne̱ shi ngbe nje,
ngbe n hwie̱ nnencwuo Krristi Jesu re nzhi nwie Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱. Nje shi ncwuo shi nyi ya prristi aha ngbe n brro re̱se̱ Nka Rina Be̱ne̱; ngbe Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ ré ci shi nyi ya teede na ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri Be̱ne̱ re se̱, ne Nshe Wiri we ko á hwie̱ na Be̱ne̱.
Aha ni nje cwe zewe ne cwuo Be̱ne̱ ne nje shi mi a yarri Krristi Jesu.
Ko shi n mahwie̱ he nje shi he ya nka we̱, se we kya ne Krristi ngu nyi a yarri nje aha ngu kwa Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ ré ne̱ ne nyi kya ne Be̱ne̱ he aha re-nka ne nje we heng ngbe re-ankya ne nje nyi,
ne igbe̱ ngbá re-sheede ngbe re-cwuong hwie̱ nga onu ne igbe̱ Nshe Be̱ne̱. Nyi aha ni ne nje ce̱ ciee a Urrushelima he̱rri re nzhi wre̱ Ilirriku nwie brro Nka Rina Krristi zhwozhwo.
Ngba cwu kya ne nje i ce̱ e̱ nyi nke he n brro Nka Rina nna a nwie ne koó ning hu Krristi gung we̱, kishi nje ri shi shi nne ne ngu shi runo a zete riti runo na yaka ya nne ngu sa.
Me̱di a shi we shi ne e wie he,<RF q=+><a href="b23.52.15 (LXX)">Ish 52:15 (LXX)</a>“Nné mbe ne koó i we ting aha ngu we̱, á ri ri,ngbe nné mbe ne ko mbe i ho we̱ wé̱ she hu re̱se̱ng.”
Bulu hwie nkang ywa a RromaA nyi aha ni ne ngu ning fo zhe we yang ne nje ce̱ be nwie nyi, me̱di koo ci we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b45.1.13">Rro 1:13</a>
Me̱di a zhe ne ne̱ tu ne nje fro re-cwuo nje a re-ngwie̱ nke ne̱, ne nje bra fo re-rie we yang nwie ku ucwua nyi he nje ra be n ya níng ri,
nje hwie he nje cwo be a zhe ne ne̱. Nje sa riyii he kundu nje ri shi rê re nzhi Sipaniya, ma n ta n níng dzie. Kundu nje ri ci e̱we̱ zhe tsie̱ ngbe ne nyi, nyi e̱ ning sheng a ciee nje re nzhi miimi e̱ fa.
Me̱di a zhe ne ne̱ nje shi rê re nzhi Urrushelima aha a bi ankya ne nje cwo a ngwa nné Be̱ne̱ a miimi.<RF q=+><a href="b46.16.1-4">1Kor 16:1-4</a>
Aha rekpri nné ce nka a Makyidoniya ngbe Akaya á ngwa nci mbe nwie tsu ncwé̱ aha yiriywé̱ ne mbe shi tsi nné Be̱ne̱ na Urrushelima.
A nyi kya ne mbe rwe nying we mwa yi mbe, wire ma aa bra mwa ye̱ye̱rri ngbe ré we sheng. Tu ne Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ e̱ mbe she mwo rina na nka Be̱ne̱ aha nné Yahudi, mahu aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri ngbe ré we sheng ne kya mbe bi ma.<RF q=+><a href="b46.9.11">1Kor 9:11</a>
Kundu nje ri fro cwuong ywa mi ne ankya ne̱, ne nje hu cence he aa ngwie nva mbe, wire ma n pie rê re nzhi Sipaniya, ma n ta n níng dzie wire n wara.
Nje hu he nje ri shi ya wre̱ nwie nyi e̱, ma n ya wre̱ ne re-mwo rina Krristi we yang.
Re-gimbe, nje cwe nva ne nyi aha Brrabe̱ nzhi Jesu Krristi ngbe ce̱ ne Nshe Be̱ne̱ ngu ci nzhi yaa ce̱: he nyi kwe̱ ngbe nje a yarri ku Be̱ne̱ aha nje.
Nyi ku he Be̱ne̱ re ning kye̱ a nva nné ra nka a Yahudi, he ngbe nné Be̱ne̱ ne mbe shi Urrushelima a ré bra ya se̱ kya ne nje cwo a we ngwa;
Nde Be̱ne̱ ne ngu ngwá srra rina re shi ngbe ne nyi zhwozhwo. Nde re shi ni.
Re-dzie BuluNje bra ce̱ nyi hu Fibi, ne ngu nyi gimbe nzhi ewerembrru, ne ngu nyi nnencwuo Be̱ne̱ a yarri ekpri nné ce̱ nka na Kenkrra.
Nyi ki se̱ a yarri lo Brrabe̱ shi ne ngu mwa ye̱ye̱rri ré ning se̱ nne Be̱ne̱. Nyi bra ki sheng ne ko nda ne ngu ri kre a nwie nyi; aha aa nyi ne she nné piriring ga ngbe nje ma.
• Nyi ning dzie Prriska ngbe Akyila, ne mbe nyi rwincwuó nje a yarri Krristi Jesu.
Á i ngwa nci mbe shi mbe shi ning kwi kwi aha nje. Nje we ci kijie̱ng, ko nyi we nje nggaa nje we̱, me̱di ga ngbe rekpri nné ce̱ nka Nné Nzhwe Ngwie̱ zhwozhwo.
• Nyi ning dzie ekpri nné ce̱ nka ne mbe mwé a ri mbe wa.• Nyi ning dzie brra rwi nje Epenetu, ne ngu i ke̱she se̱ nka Krristi a mbè ngwie̱ Asia.
• Nyi ning dzie Merri ne ngu i nyi cwuo we yang aha nyi.
