Aha nzhi e̱ we nci nzhi ma, nzhi i nyi mwa, nzhi i ra ho nka. Á i níng brra, nzhi hwie̱ ꞌhwié na ga re-nzhwe ankya ne nzhi kre ngbe ga re-nzhwe ecwue ngwie̱. Nzhi i srra yarri ngwie̱ngwie̱ ne rehwie rro; yá i níng ra, nzhi e̱ we ra ma.
Me̱di zhe ne Be̱ne̱ ne ngu nyi Nnenkyia nzhi e̱ ya níng ti zhwe ehwie rina ngu ngbe ce̱ ne ngu níng ce̱,
