Ga ngbe Marrku, ngbe Arristaku, ngbe Dema, ngbe Luka ne mbe nyi rwincwuó nje e̱ á re dzie.<RF q=+><a href="b44.12.12">RNné 12:12</a>, <a href="b44.12.25">25</a>; <a href="b44.13.13">13:13</a>; <a href="b44.15.37-39">15:37-39</a>; <a href="b44.19.29">19:29</a>; <a href="b44.27.2">27:2</a>; <a href="b51.4.10">Kol 4:10</a>, <a href="b51.4.14">14</a>; <a href="b55.4.10">2Tim 4:10</a>, <a href="b55.4.11">11</a>
Nde ehwie rina Brrabe̱ Jesu Krristi re shi ngbe nyi.
<font color=teal>Krre̱de̱ re nzhi nwie Nné Ibrrani</font>Be̱ne̱ ti rici ngu ne Kowe nguGbangba tiya, Be̱ne̱ i he yó nzhi nka a re-zhe piriri a re-rê kanka kanka a nu nné ti re̱se̱ng.
Me̱di a rotu krrucing ne̱, aa he nka ne nzhi ne Kowe ngu. Be̱ne̱ i nyi ebe ngwie̱ zhwozhwo<RF q=+>ebe ngwie̱ zhwozhwo:Ko nyi we ebe ngwie̱ we̱, me̱di ngbe zinye̱, ngbe ko nda ne e nyi. ne ngu, aa bra ki kyie aha ngbe ko nda re hwie̱ na ngu.
A nyi ngu ngu nyi nse̱ na grime̱ Be̱ne̱, a bra nyi ngu ne ngu nyi cwu cwu shî Be̱ne̱ ne ngu bró ngwie̱ ne̱ zhwozhwo ne riti nka ngu ne ngu bi igbe̱. A zhe ne ngu níng yi re-e̱ngwie̱ nzhi, aa ya srra zinye̱ a nva nyye Be̱ne̱ ne ngu bi brra grime̱.
Jesu ne̱ re-njeliAha ni ngu Kowe e̱ she grime̱ re ne̱ re-njeli aha lo ne e ki ngwa a ne̱ re-na mbe.
Ka nyi zohu a tsi re-njeli e̱ ne Be̱ne̱ sa he ne ngu he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.2.7">Rve 2:7</a>; <a href="b10.7.14">2Sam 7:14</a>; <a href="b13.17.13">1NTiy 17:13</a>“Ngwe̱ nyi Kowe nje;a cwu ne̱ nje hwie̱ ꞌBe̱ ngwe̱”?Ka re he ne ngu he,“Nje cwo a hwie̱ ꞌBe̱ ngwe̱,ngbe ngwe̱ e̱ bra hwie̱ Kowe nje” e̱e̱?
Me̱di zhe ne ngu shi ning brru be ne ce̱ucwu Kowe ngu a be ngwie̱, a he:<RF q=+><a href="b5.32.43 (LXX)">NNMN 32:43 (LXX)</a>“Nde ga re-njeli Be̱ne̱ zhwozhwo ré ki ye mbè.”
Me̱di ne re-njeli e̱, Be̱ne̱ he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.104.4 (LXX)">Rve 104:4 (LXX)</a>“Be̱ne̱ cí re-njeli ngu ré shi shi wu,ngbe nnencwuó ngu a wé̱ shi shi le ndo.”
Ngbe ne Kowe e̱, Be̱ne̱ e̱ he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.45.6-7">Rve 45:6-7</a>“Be̱ne̱, ringgwe̱ ngwe̱ e̱ ri shi he̱rri tiya tiya,ngbo ringgwe̱ ngwe̱ e̱bra ri nyi ngbo na ncwuo redziee.
Ngwe̱ ce̱ redziee, ngwe̱ e̱ ra ꞌhwie̱.Kya a nyi ngwiee ne Be̱ne̱ ne ngu nyi Be̱ne̱ ngwe̱,ngu re fo ze re ne̱ ga re-nda ngwe̱,a zhe ne ngu re mia ne ehwie kla.”
A bra he wa he,“Brrabe̱, tu ce̱ucwung,nyi ngwe̱ ngwe̱ i sa riti ebe ngwie̱,ga ngbe re-zinye̱ e̱ á nyi cwuo nva ngwe̱.
Á cwo a ci shweni,me̱di ngwe̱ e̱ ngwe̱ ning shi;mbe e̱ á shi kre shi shi nyi ankya ci.
Ngwe̱ ri we krru shi shi nyi ya brra tago,ngbe ga mbe zhwozhwo á riwe cenja shi shi ankya ci.Me̱di ko ngwe̱ e̱ ngwe̱ bra we̱,ko re-rie ngwe̱ bi krrucing we̱.”
A nyi zohu a tsi re-njeli e̱ ne Be̱ne̱ sa he ne ngu he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.110.1">Rve 110:1</a>“Srra a nva nyye nje,se nje re ci ngwe̱ hle̱ rwinkó ngwe̱”?
Ko ga re-njeli e̱ zhwozhwo nyi nnencwuó Be̱ne̱ we̱ e̱e̱? Koó we ri we̱, me̱di nyi mbe ne Be̱ne̱ ngu we ci ré she nné mbe ne mbe ri she kyia.
Brra kyiaKya a nyi nke ngu ci aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri ngbe nzhi ning bra bro kya ne nzhi i ho a gangga, kishi nzhi ri ning brru ne emerin.
Nka ne re-njeli mbe i he e̱ shi ni cence, á ri ngwa ko zohu nne e̱ngwie̱ ngbe nne ra ho nka ge̱zhe̱ aha kya ne mbe nyi.
He̱rri nzhi e̱ ri ce̱ rimi nzhi to kye̱, kundu ne nzhi ra ci nkwile̱ ne brra kyia ne e níng ngwa ne̱ ye̱? Brrabe̱ we rici ngu i ke̱she ti nka kyia ne̱, ngbe nné mbe ne mbe i ho a mbe e̱ ti cence he shi ni.
We̱sa a ni, Be̱ne̱ e̱ bra ning bra ya sheede a zeteng ne ngbá re-sheede, ngbe ngbá re-ankya ne ngu nyi, ngbe re-cwuong hwie̱ nga onu nzhwenzhweng, ngbe re-beewa Nshe Wiri ne ngu kye ye̱ye̱rri ne kya ce̱ ngu.
Nne ne ngu níng be ne kyiaKo nyi re-njeli ne Be̱ne̱ i we sa ré hwie̱ nné ye ringgwe̱ ngwie̱ hwi ne ngu cwo be we̱, ngu ngwie̱ ne nzhi ning shi nka ne̱.
Me̱di a bi ewie ne e ning wieng a yarri krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ he:<RF q=+><a href="b19.8.4-6 (LXX)">Rve 8:4-6 (LXX)</a>“Brrabe̱, nyi nda ngu nyi nneywi e̱,ne he̱rri ngwe̱ lú aha ngu aa?Nyi nda ngu nyi kowe nneywi e̱,ne he̱rri ngwe̱ cí nkwile̱ ne ngu aa?
Ngwe̱ ki nyi aa re̱ tsie̱ re shi shi re-njeli a e̱we̱ zhe tsie̱nzhwu;ngwe̱ ki fo ze ngwe̱ ki ngwa grime̱.
Me̱di nzhi ri Jesu ne a e̱we̱ zhe tsie̱nzhwu á i ki ci re re̱ tsie̱ ne re-njeli, ngbe aha a yarri ehwie rina Be̱ne̱ re hu aha ko nye̱, me̱di a zhe ne ne̱ á ki ci vo ringgwe̱, á ki fo ze á ki ngwa grime̱, aha ge̱zhe̱ hu ne ngu shwe.
A i mwa ye̱ye̱rri a nwie Be̱ne̱ ne ngu nyi ga ankya zhwozhwo, ne ga ankya zhwozhwo bra ning shi aha ngu, he ngbe ngu ci nne ne ngu we be ne kyia re fro cwuo ngu ye̱ye̱rri a yarri ge̱zhe̱ ne ngu shwe. Aa nyi ni aha ngu ci rewe ngu piriri ré she grime̱ ngu.
Ngu ne ngu ci ga nneywí ci wiriri, ngbe mbe ne e we ci mbe ci wiriri e̱ gbengbe á mwe á hwie̱ rewe ꞌBe̱ zunzrru. Kya a nyi ngwiee ko nyi kya nshwu we̱ a nwie Jesu ngbe ngu we ye he re-gimbe ngu.
A he ne ꞌBe̱ e̱ he,“Nje ri ti re-gimbe nje lo ngwe̱,nje ri ve ve nwie re de a yarri ekpri mbe.”
A he wa he, “Nje ri yaa nyenyi a Be̱ne̱.”A bra he wa he,“Nje e̱ nke ne, ngbe ne rewe ne Be̱ne̱ ngu ning ngwa.”<RF q=+><a href="b23.8.17">Ish 8:17</a>, <a href="b23.8.18">18</a>
Tu ne rewe nna mbe nyi rine̱ ne roshwo, aha ni a i ci shi mbe ma, ne ngu i fo shî nneywi; a i nyi ni ngbe aha hu ngu, ngu ci Nne ꞌHwie̱ ana re ci shweni, ngu ne ngu bi igbe̱ng ci nneywí ré kwi e̱.
A nyi ni ne ngu ci nné mbe ne gannyi mbe i nyi ꞌhwié aha ne mbe to owu hu mbe she drre̱.
A shi we gbeng he ko nyi re-njeli ne Jesu a i be we sheng we̱, me̱di nyi nzhwe Ibrrahin.<RF q=+><a href="b23.41.8-9">Ish 41:8-9</a>
A nyi aha ni ne i ki ci re hwie̱ we shi re-gimbe ngu a ko zohu eme, aha ngbe re hwie̱ brra prristi ne ngu bi naana, ne e bra hung sa rie a ngu a ncwuo Be̱ne̱, aha re nyi teedeng we re-e̱ngwie̱ nneywí.
Aha tu ne ngu we rici ngu ngu shwe ge̱zhe̱ re-mwa ri, mahu we̱ hung she nné mbe ne mbe shi she mwa ri ma.
Jesu a ne̱ MusaAha ni re-gimbe ne Be̱ne̱ e̱ níng kyie nzhi hwie̱ nné wiri ngu, nyi sa hwie nka nyi a Jesu ne ngu nyi nnente ngbe brra prristi ne nzhi sa rie a ngu shi ne nzhi tí we gbeng.
A i nyi tsantsa ne kya ne Be̱ne̱ i ki ci re nyi, ye̱ye̱rri we shi Musa ne ngu i nyi tsantsa a ncwuo ngu a yarri eri Be̱ne̱ ma.<RF q=+><a href="b4.12.7">HNné 12:7</a>
Jesu a ne̱ Musa ne grime̱ we yang we shi nne ne ngu no eri bi grime̱ we yang re ne̱ eri nna.
Ko zohu eri e̱ bi nne nong, me̱di nyi Be̱ne̱ ngu no ko nda.
Musa i nyi nnencwuo ne ngu shi tsantsa a yarri ncwuo eri Be̱ne̱, a i ke̱nce̱ ngwa sheede re-ankya ne Be̱ne̱ ri he a re-zhe na ncwuee.
Me̱di Krristi e̱ yo tsantsa a nu Kowe ne ngu bró eri Be̱ne̱. Nzhi e̱ nzhi nyi eri ngu, kundu ne nzhi yaa rwe, nzhi bra yo gangga a zete kya ne nzhi ning sa riyii.
Nné Be̱ne̱ á ri she srra cwuAha nii, we shi kya ne Nshe Wiri he:<RF q=+><a href="b19.95.7-11 (LXX)">Rve 95:7-11 (LXX)</a>“A cwu, kundu ne nyi ho cwue ngu,
shi de̱ nyi klo nci we̱,kishi nyi ri nyi zhwe gbanggrraa yó nyi,a zhe ne mbe i mwa Be̱ne̱ ri a tsi yi.
Be̱ne̱ he, a miimi e̱ á i ning mwahe mbe ri ka nje shi rimi ye̱,ko ngbe ne mbe i ri re-ankyane nje i nyi a re-rie nshwa weni.
Kya a nyi ngwiee ne nje i dzioehwie ne nné mbe ana,nje e̱ he,‘Á we rê a yarri ronu rie mbe,koó bra ce̱ hu re-rê nje we̱.’
Aha ni a yarri ehwie dzio, nje fo shí he:‘Koó bi ngwie a ngwie̱ng srra cwu nje e̱ we̱.’ ”
Re-gimbe, nyi ci nkwile̱, shi de̱ e̱ngwie̱ ngbe riywe̱ shî nka a yarri onu rie ya nyi re ki ci re bra teme re ngwa Be̱ne̱ bi ce we̱.
Me̱di nyi yaa shwe̱ rehwie ko zohu otu; nyi ning tu rici ni a ko zohu otu ne e hung ki ye he, “A cwu ne̱”, kishi e̱ngwie̱ ri brra ya nyi he̱rri re ne̱ ne klo rici.
Kundu nzhi yo gangga ne sa rie nzhi he̱rri re nzhi cwu gamang shi ne nzhi i ce̱ a ce̱ucwung, nzhi e̱ ri mwe nzhi she ko nda ne Krristi ngu bi aha nzhi.
A shi we shi ne e he he,“A cwu, kundu nyi ho cwue ngu,shi de̱ nyi klo nci shi shi yónzhi mbe i nyi we̱,shi a zhe ne mbe i nyi Be̱ne̱ gbanggrraa.”
Nyi mbe nye̱ ne mbe i ho cwue Be̱ne̱ gbengbe ni mbe ki nyi gbanggrraa a? Ko nyi ga nné mbe ne Musa i wru ne mbe a Masarr we̱ e̱e̱?<RF q=+><a href="b4.14.1-35">HNné 14:1-35</a>
A nyi mbe nye̱ ne Be̱ne̱ i dzio ehwie ne mbe he̱rri re-rie nshwa weni e̱? Ko nyi nné mbe ne mbe i nyi e̱ngwie̱, ne he̱rri mbe kwi a tsi yi we̱ e̱e̱?
A bra nyi mbe nye̱ ne Be̱ne̱ i fo shí ne mbe he koó bi ngwie a ngwie̱ng she srra cwu ngu we̱ e̱? Ko nyi nné mbe ne mbe i ra ki ho nka we̱ e̱e̱?
Aha ni nzhi ri he koó i she ngwie we̱ aha ne ko mbe i bi sa rie we̱.
Aha nzhi i ho Nka Rina ne e níng brrong we shi ne mbe ho ma; me̱di mbe e̱, ko nka nna we be ne yankya rina we̱, aha a zhe ne mbe i ho, koó se̱ ne ning sa rie we̱.
Aha a nyi we nzhi ne nzhi bi sa rie ne nzhi ri ngwie nwieng srra cwu, we shi ne Be̱ne̱ i he ne kpi nné he:<RF q=+><a href="b19.95.11">Rve 95:11</a>“Aha ni nje dzio ehwie ne mbe,nje e̱ fo shí he,‘Koó bi ngwie a nwieng she srra cwu nje ana we̱.’ ”A i he nka ne̱ ko ngbe ne ngu fro ko nda a zhe ne ngu i nyi ebe ngwie̱ yhwe̱.
A ya ewie a yarri Krre̱de̱ Be̱ne̱ á he nka aha otu na natsie̱ he: “A otu na natsie̱, Be̱ne̱ srra cwu ne re-cwuo ngu zhwozhwo.”<RF q=+><a href="b1.2.2">Ce̱u 2:2</a>
Shi a nka ne̱ wa á bra ning brru he wa he, “Koó bi ngwie a nwieng srra cwu nje we̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b19.95.11">Rve 95:11</a>
Tu ne e we he yá bi we ngwie a yarri srra cwu ana, nné mbe ne mbe i ke̱she ho Nka Rina ne e brro a koó she ngwie we̱, aha riywe̱ sa rie mbe,
aha ni Be̱ne̱ cinga sa yaka otu, ne ngu ki ye he “A cwu”. Re-rie piriri wara wire ngu ya he nka a yarri krre̱de̱ re-ve Dooda, shi ne e ke̱she he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.95.7-8 (LXX)">Rve 95:7-8 (LXX)</a>“A Cwu, kundu nyi ho cwue ngu,shi de̱ nyi klo nci we̱.”
Kundu Joshwua i ra we ngwa srra cwu, ko Be̱ne̱ i ra cinga he nka aha yaka otu wa we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b5.31.7">NNMN 31:7</a>; <a href="b6.22.4">Jos 22:4</a>
Mahu gbengbe ni, a cwo a bi Otung Srra Cwu aha nné Be̱ne̱.
Aha ko nye̱ ne ngu ri she ngwie a srra cwu Be̱ne̱ ana, mahu a ri she srra cwu ne ga re-cwuo ngu, we shi ne Be̱ne̱ i srra cwu ma.<RF q=+><a href="b1.2.2">Ce̱u 2:2</a>
Aha ni nde nzhi tu rici aha ngbe nzhi hung ngwie a srra cwu ana, kishi ya nzhi ri grre̱ shi ne mbe i nyi aha riywe̱ sa rie mbe.
Aha nka Be̱ne̱ e̱ bi ce ngbe igbe̱, a yé re ne̱ ise̱nkeli bi reme wehwie pempempee. A ngwi he̱rri yarri yarring re nzhi cwu nu rie ngbe nshe, he̱rri re nzhi cwu yarri re-hwon ngbe brrugo. He̱rri aa hung hu ga re-hwie nka nzhi ngbe ankya ne rehwie nzhi ce̱.
Ko bi ko yankya ngu shi la la a nyyi Be̱ne̱ we̱. Ko nda shi gang we gbeng a nyyi ngu, ngu ne ga nzhi zhwozhwo nzhi ri yo nzhi he ga re-ankya ne nzhi nyi.
Jesu nyi Brra Prristi brrabrrangAha nii, tu ne nzhi bi Brra Prristi brrabrrang, ne ngu nyi Jesu Kowe Be̱ne̱, ne ngu ywa he̱rri nyyi Be̱ne̱, nde nzhi yo gangga a kya ne nzhi ning sa rie ne nzhi he we gbeng.
Ko Brra Prristi nzhi e̱ nyi ya nne ngu we̱sa ri naana nzhi ne re̱ nzhi we̱. Me̱di Brra Prristi nzhi e̱ á i ki mwa ri a ko zohu rê we shi nzhi e̱ ma, gbengbe ni koo ree nyi e̱ngwie̱ we̱.
Aha nii, nde nzhi yaa wa nzhi be nyyi ncwu ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ ne ngu bi ehwie rina we dengge, ngbe re ri naana nzhi. Wire nzhi e̱ she ehwie rina ngu, we̱ bra níng sheng a zhe ne nzhi kre re níng sheng.
Á kyié ko zohu brra prristi a tsi kpi nné aha re nyi cwuo Be̱ne̱ a nu mbe, aha ngbe re hwie̱ nne si re-ankya na na mbe re ngwa Be̱ne̱, re bra nyi re-teede aha re-e̱ngwie̱ mbe.
Aa hung kwa nné riywe̱ hung ngbe nné mbe ne mbe brru rê e̱ we sheng, aha ngu a we rici ngu ngu re̱ ma.
Kya a nyi ngwiee ne ko nyi re-teede e̱ we aha re-e̱ngwie̱ na nneywí we̱, me̱di aha na ngu ma.<RF q=+><a href="b3.9.7">Liv 9:7</a>
Ko ya nne kré grime̱ng hwie̱ brra prristi we rici ngu we̱, se ka nyi Be̱ne̱ ngu ki ye shi ne ngu i ye Arruna.<RF q=+><a href="b2.28.1">Wru 28:1</a>
A shi ni wa, ko Krristi e̱ i kre grime̱ng hwie̱ Brra Prristi we rici ngu we̱. Me̱di Be̱ne̱ i he ne ngu he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.2.7">Rve 2:7</a>“Ngwe̱ nyi Kowe nje;a cwu ne̱ nje hwie̱ ꞌBe̱ ngwe̱.”
Aa bra he a yaka ewie wa he,<RF q=+><a href="b19.110.4">Rve 110:4</a>“Ngwe̱ nyi Prristi he̱rri tiya,ngwe̱ nyi prristi we shi Melkyizede.”<RF q=+>we shi Melkyizede:Kaa nwie Melkyizede.
A zhe ne Jesu i srra a be ngwie̱, a i mwo rumwo nwie cwe nva ne brra riwie̱ng cwue, he̱rri ngbe ne reyii re nzhi nwie Be̱ne̱, ne ngu hung ki kye̱ ne hu. Be̱ne̱ i ki hong aha ne ngu yaa ci re̱, ngu bra ngwa rici.<RF q=+><a href="b40.26.36-46">Mat 26:36-46</a>; <a href="b41.14.32-42">Mar 14:32-42</a>; <a href="b42.22.39-46">Luk 22:39-46</a>
Me̱di ko ngbe ne ngu nyi Kowe Be̱ne̱, aa mie̱ ho nka a yarri re-ge̱zhe̱ ne ngu i shwe.
A zhe ne ngu fro ko nda, ngu a hwie̱ rêng she ce na he̱rri tiya a nwie ga nné mbe ne mbe ki ho nka,
a zhe ne Be̱ne̱ i ki ci re hwie̱ brra prristi we shi Melkyizede.
Shi de̱ nyi we ni sa rie a Krristi we̱Nzhi bi kya he we yang a nka ne̱, me̱di a bi rwe̱ ré níng ting he̱rri nyi pie aha ko nyi hung pie kya we hwiehwie we̱.
Aa mwa ye̱ye̱rri a zhe ne ne̱ nyi ra hwie̱ nné mie̱ nka, me̱di he̱rri ne cwu se ka ré bra cinga níng mie̱ e̱we̱e̱ re-ankya na nka Be̱ne̱. Ko nyi ci ré níng ngwa cwu yâ we̱, se ka ré níng ngwa we madrra!<RF q=+><a href="b46.3.2">1Kor 3:2</a>
Aha nne nke ne ngu rishi ka shwe we madrra a, a ka nyi we e̱we̱we ne ko ngu hu shwong ka kye̱ng we̱, koo hu cwuo redziee ngbe kya ngu shi wie̱e̱ni we̱.
Me̱di cwu yâ a nyi na nné mbe ne mbe hu kwe, aha ne mbe mie̱ mbe hu re̱se̱ cwuo redziee ngbe me̱nkye̱ng, á bra hung kyie kya ne ngu shi ye̱ye̱rri.
ga ngbe nkang nyi batisma, ne e garra nneywí nva we̱; ngbe nkang vu nné kwi, ngbe nyi nka ne e ri nyi he̱rri tiya we̱.
Nde nzhi ci brráng, kundu Be̱ne̱ e̱ níng ngwa riwie̱! Kya ne nzhi shi nying nna nyi ngwiee.
Wé̱ ce̱ rimi ngbe nne nke ne i ki ci ngu hu raywrra Be̱ne̱ re bra se̱ ywe̱ te̱nte̱ wa ye̱? Ngu ne ngu ho shwi kya na na ne ngu wru zinye̱, ne he̱rri ngu i she igbe̱ Nshe Wiri,
ne ngu bra ree ho shwi rina nka Be̱ne̱, ngbe ne igbe̱<RF q=+>igbe̱:Kaigbe̱ ringgwe̱ Be̱ne̱ ... na ꞌzhe ne ngu cwo be,
kundu ngu we rê, ko bi re bra ning brru re se̱ ywe̱ te̱nte̱ we̱, aha ne ngu we rici ngu a shi nwie ning brru ci Kowe Be̱ne̱ a gasankwe te̱nte̱ wa, nwie ki ci nshwu we gbeng.
Ebe ne ngu shé nze cwucwu nwie ning ci yâ kpe̱kpe̱ aha nné kye̱ng, Be̱ne̱ ki mwo rina.
Me̱di ebe nke ne ngu cí we re-ze̱kye̱ ngbe ne re-canci e̱ shi we dede, Be̱ne̱ ri ki ci re ci shweni, we̱ ning ci ro.<RF q=+><a href="b1.3.17-18">Ce̱u 3:17-18</a>
Nné ce̱ nje, me̱di ko ngbe ne nzhi he ni, nzhi hu cence he nyi bi ankya te̱nte̱ng ne ngu nyi na kyia.
Ko Be̱ne̱ nyi riywe̱ redziee we̱; kundu ga re ki bru ne re-cwuo nyi ngbe ce̱ ne nyi ti he nyi ki ce̱ we̱, shi ne nyi shé nné ngung, ne nyi bra fo he nyi shi ke̱ we ne we sheng.
Ngba cwu kya ne nzhi ce̱ e̱ nyi nke he, ko nye̱ a tsi nyi re ke̱ we ne ning tu rici ni he̱rri re nzhi cwu krrucing, aha ngbe nyi hung sa riyii tsantsa a kya ne nyi cwo a sheng.
Ko nzhi ce̱ nyi bi rê we̱, me̱di nyi shi shi nné mbiye ne mbe bi sa rie ngbe ehwie sheng, ne mbe she kya ne Be̱ne̱ i we sa ꞌjee aha ni.
