Me̱di ngu Krristi e̱ nyi teede nang yi re-e̱ngwie̱ nneywí we ce ꞌzrru he̱rri tiya, ngbe ngu a ya srra a nva nyye Be̱ne̱.<RF q=+><a href="b19.110.1">Rve 110:1</a>
