We ne teede zunzrru ana, aa ci nné mbiye ne e we ci mbe ci wiri ne e̱ngwie̱ á ci tsantsa he̱rri tiya.
Nshe Wiri e̱ bra níng ngwá sheede wa. Aa ke̱she he,
“ꞌJee ne nje shi sang ne mbe<RF q=+><a href="b24.31.33">Iri 31:33</a>a rotu ngu cwo be e̱ nyi nke, Brrabe̱ he ni:Nje ri ci nti nka nje a yarri ronu rie mbengbe ma n wie a yarri rehwie mbe.”
Ngu a ning brang he, “Ko ma n bra lu ne re-e̱ngwie̱ mbe ngbe ne riywe̱ zhwe nti nka mbe wa we̱.”<RF q=+><a href="b24.31.34">Iri 31:34</a>
Aha ni tu ne e we we ga re-ankya ne̱ mahu ko bi ya teede ne e bra shi cinga nying aha e̱ngwie̱ wa we̱.
Nzhi shwo re be dudu ne Be̱ne̱Aha nii, re-gimbe, roshwo Jesu a níng ngwa riwie̱ng ngwie a Nwie Wiri Kaka we dengge.
Aa níng kla ya rê hwi, ne ngu shi nce, ne ngu cie̱ yarri brra trro gbundu, mahu nyi rwe̱ na ngu.
Nzhi bi Brra Prristi ne ngu cí nkwile̱ ne eri Be̱ne̱.
Aha ni nde nzhi shwo re be dudu ne Be̱ne̱ ne raywrra a yarri ronu rie nzhi ngbe ne sa rie a ngu we̱sa ne nyi jinji, ne ronu rie nzhi ne e níng kprre̱ roshwo Krristi aha ngbe nzhi ci wiriri ngbe nzhi hu he á níng we re-e̱ngwie̱ nzhi, ne ga ngbe re-rwe̱ nzhi ne e we kyu wiriri ne rishi cwancwaa.<RF q=+><a href="b3.8.30">Liv 8:30</a>; <a href="b26.36.25">Ezi 36:25</a>
Nde nzhi yo ne igbe̱ nwie ke̱ we ne sa riyii a kya ne nzhi brró, aha ngu Be̱ne̱ ne ngu níng sa ꞌjee e̱ aa be nzhi hung sa rie a ngu.
Nde nzhi hwie re-rêng yaa shwe̱ rehwie a nci nzhi, ngbe nzhi yaa ce̱ nwie nyi re-cwuo rina.
Shi de̱ nzhi we ni mwe gbengbe we̱, shi yá ne mbe fo zhwe e̱kpe̱e̱ ana; me̱di nzhi ning bra yaa shwe̱ rehwie — shi re ngra ning hwie̱ ne nzhi ri Otu Brrabe̱ ngu sa dudu ne̱.
Kundu nzhi ke̱ we ne nyi e̱ngwie̱ we igerri a zhe ne nzhi i she hu re̱se̱ nka raywrra, ko bra bi ya teedeng yi e̱ngwie̱ ne e ri bra nyi wa we̱,
se we srra ne owu nwie tsio nyi nka ngbe brra ro ne ngu ri ye nné mbe ne mbe nyi rwinkó Be̱ne̱.<RF q=+><a href="b23.26.11 (LXX)">Ish 26:11 (LXX)</a>
