Ma nyi hwie he nné mbe ne mbe dzié̱ Kowe Be̱ne̱, ne ko mbe ri roshwo na ꞌjee ne ngu níng ci nzhi ci wiri e̱ a nu yankya we̱, ne mbe bra he nka shweni ne Nshe Wiri ne ngu níng be ne ehwie rina Be̱ne̱, ge̱zhe̱ ne e ri we ngwa a ri ngra shi rimi e̱e̱?<RF q=+><a href="b2.24.8">Wru 24:8</a>
