Sa rieSa rie e̱ nyi hu re̱se̱ng kpe̱kpe̱ he nzhi shi she kya ne nzhi ning sa riyii, a nyi kya ne nzhi hu he a shi ni ko ngbe ne ko nzhi ri ne riyii we̱.
A nyi aha sa rie ne Be̱ne̱ i de nné tiya.
A nyi aha sa rie ne nzhi hu he Be̱ne̱ i nyi ebe ngwie̱ zhwozhwo ne riti nka ngu, mahu á i nyi kya ne nzhi ri ne̱ ne kya ne koó ri we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b1.1.1">Ce̱u 1:1</a>; <a href="b19.33.6">Rve 33:6</a>, <a href="b19.33.9">9</a>; <a href="b43.1.3">Yoh 1:3</a>
