He̱rri ne cwu, ko ngbe re-ꞌbe̱ nzhi na be ngwie̱ he ne mbe níng na uucwu, ko nzhi we ngwa grime̱ aha ni we̱ e̱e̱? Ma nzhi e̱ shi ngra ngwa ꞌBe̱ nzhi a zinye̱ nci nzhi rimi, ngbe nzhi she ce he̱rri tiya a?
Re-ꞌbe̱ nzhi na be ngwie̱ e̱ á níng na uucwu a e̱we̱ zhe tsie̱nzhwu, shi ne mbe ri aa we mwa ye̱ye̱rri, me̱di Be̱ne̱ níng na uucwu aha re níng sheng, aha ngbe nzhi ci wiri shi ngu.
A zhe ne e shi níng na uucwu, ko we̱ níng bi rina a zheng nna we̱, aha a wié. Me̱di a ncwuee, lede nna cwo a nyi srra rina ngbe e̱kpe̱e̱ redziee a nwie nné mbiye ne mbe mie̱ a zhe ne e shi we na uucwu.
