Nyi ci nkwile̱ ne ko nye̱ a tsi nyi kishi ya nyi ri wi ehwie rina Be̱ne̱. Shi de̱ ya nyi re bra hwie̱ shi shi rinyie ya ekwe rro rro ne ngu shi ci, re bra dzio re̱se̱ kpi nyi we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b5.29.18 (LXX)">NNMN 29:18 (LXX)</a>
