Á a he ne mbe he shi de̱ ré re ko ya ntsi ka yaka yankya ne e tsi, ka ya ekwe we̱, se we nné mbe ne koó we ci ce̱e̱le̱ Be̱ne̱ a re-teyii mbe we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b26.9.4">Ezi 9:4</a>
Koó we we ré yhwi nné nna we̱, me̱di se ré we ngwa we cinci he̱rri nyhwe̱ wecwuoo. Zhwe ge̱zhe̱ ne mbe shwe e̱ a wié shi shi na nnywa te nné.
A rotu ana nneywí ri kre he mbe kwi, me̱di koó ri she we̱. Á ri me̱ he mbe ce̱ hu, me̱di hu a ri we to.<RF q=+><a href="b18.3.21">Ayu 3:21</a>; <a href="b24.8.3">Iri 8:3</a>
Re-iigye nna á shi shi ntsié̱ ne mbe srrante aha cwe. Á bi yankyá a nci mbe shi shi nyi re-vo ringgwe̱ na zinarriya, nyyi mbe e̱ shi shi na nneywí.<RF q=+><a href="b29.2.4">Yow 2:4</a>
Nkwe rici mbe shi shi na mbrrú; nnyi mbe e̱ shi shi na re-ze̱kyi.<RF q=+><a href="b29.1.6">Yow 1:6</a>
Á bi re-tagong ku zewe shi shi nyi na kprincwe̱, re̱zhe̱ re-gahaan mbe shi shi rogyrru ntsie̱ piriri ngbe re-eekyie ntsie̱ ne mbe nyia rrutututu re nzhi kwe̱ cwe.<RF q=+><a href="b29.2.5">Yow 2:5</a>
Á bi re-runcwo, á bra te nné shi shi nnywa te nné, á bi igbe̱ng ngwa nneywí cinci ne re-runcwo mbe he̱rri nyhwe̱ wecwuoo.
Á bi nggwe̱ na mbe ne ngu nyi njeli na ruvo we̱sa krrucing, ne e ye lo ngu a zhe Ibrrani he Abado, a zhe nka Heleni á ki ye he Apoliyo, woto he “Nne Yhwi Nné”.
Ge̱zhe̱ na ce̱ucwung ne̱ wara, aa hwie̱ re-ge̱zhe̱ wehwie ne mbe rishi be.
Ngbe njeli na rritsie̱ e̱ yhwa rigbe na ngu, nje e̱ ho ya cwue ngu wru a re-rite na kre briing nyi teede ne e nyi ne zinarriya ne ngu shi nyyi Be̱ne̱.<RF q=+><a href="b2.30.1-3">Wru 30:1-3</a>
Cwue nna he ne njeli na rritsie̱ ne ngu bi rigbe e̱ he, “Wrru mi ne re-njeli weni ne e we rrwe a brra riywi Yuferreti ana!”
Nje e̱ ho he rigbre re-shezhi kwe̱ ne ntsié̱ nna á cwu ngba ꞌci nnywa wehwie.
Ntsié̱ ngbe nné tong ne nje ri a kya ne Be̱ne̱ ngu ning ting nna shi he ni: re-tago kprincwe̱ng ku re-zewe mbe e̱ á shi zhwuuzhwuu shi lendo, yá shi brumbru riinriin, yá a nyi rishi kwini shi shi lendo kye̱. Nci ntsié̱ nna á shi shi na re-ze̱kyi; ngbe ro ngbe ncwu ngbe lendo kye̱ e̱ wrru a ronu mbe.
Ngbá re-ge̱zhe̱ wetsie̱ na ro, ngbe ncwu, ngbe lendo kye̱ ne mbe wrru a ronu mbe e̱ á yhwi zunzrru a tsi wetsie̱ na nneywí zhwozhwo.
Aha igbe̱ ntsié̱ nna shi a ronu mbe ngbe a re-runcwo mbe. Re-runcwo mbe e̱ á shi shi nyi nshé, he̱rri á bi nci ne mbe ning tsie̱ nneywí.
Gbengbe ni, re̱se̱ nné mbiye ne ko ngbá re-ge̱zhe̱ wetsie̱ ne̱ mbe we yhwi we̱ á ra si ywe̱ ne re-ankya ne mbe nyi ne nva mbe. Koó we ni ye rewienci mbè we̱, ga ngbe re-kpanshwu zinarriya, ngbe na azrrufa, ngbe na kprincwe̱ shwo, ngbe na rahwan ngbe rekwe — re-kpanshwu ne ko mbe ri ewie we̱, koó ho nka we̱, koó bra cwo ciee we̱.<RF q=+><a href="b19.115.4-7">Rve 115:4-7</a>; <a href="b19.135.15-17">135:15-17</a>; <a href="b27.5.23">Dan 5:23</a>
Koó bra si ywe̱ ne yhwi nné, ngbe itsie, ngbe re-le̱le̱ njè, ngbe nyi nca ne mbe nyi we̱.
Njeli ngbe e̱we̱ iishi tekpeng wie cwuoWire nje e̱ ri ya brra njeli bi igbe̱ ngu wru zinye̱ ngu wró. Inyie̱ ki ku shi nyi ankya ci ne aakwrra nze a zete rici ngu. Riyii ngu a shi shi ꞌne̱, nta ngu a shi shi re-iita runo ne mbe nyi lendo.
Ngu a bro ya e̱we̱ tekpeng wie cwuo ne e ki kla a nva ngu. Aa sa ta nyye ngu a zete brra nzhwo rishi, ngu a sa ta mie ngu a ebe.
Ngu a ci onu ne brra riwie̱ng cwue shi shi nyi rugwrraa ze̱kyi. A zhe ne ngu ci ye, ngbe re-eeze natsie̱ e̱ ne̱ ne kpe ru nwie shing.
We ne mbe shî, nje e̱ ce̱ ne̱ ne wieng, me̱di nje e̱ bra ho ya cwue ne ngu wru zinye̱ he, “La kya ne re-eeze natsie̱ ana mbe he, shi de̱ ngwe̱ wie we̱!”
Ngbe njeli na ne nje ri ngu yó a zete brra nzhwo rishi ngbe a ebe ngu a gbi va nyye ze re nzhi zinye̱.<RF q=+><a href="b2.20.11">Wru 20:11</a>; <a href="b5.32.40">NNMN 32:40</a>; <a href="b27.12.7">Dan 12:7</a>; <a href="b30.3.7">Emo 3:7</a>
Ngu a fo shí ne ngwiee ne ngu nyi na bi ce gannyi tiya he̱rri tiya tiya a, ne ngu nyi zinye̱ ne ko nda ngu ning shi, ngbe ebe ngwie̱ ne ko nda ngu ning shi, ngbe brra nzhwo rishi ne ko nda ngu ning shi, ngu a he, “Ko bra shi bi dzio zhe wa we̱!
Me̱di rotu ne njeli na natsie̱ ri shi yhwa rigbe na ngu, kya la la Be̱ne̱ ri ci we shi ne ngu i ti ꞌhwié ngung, nné ti re̱se̱ng.”
Ngbe cwue ne ngu wru zinye̱ ne nje ho ngu he nka aa cinga ning he nka wa he: “Ywa ngwe̱ ya fo e̱we̱ tekpeng wie cwuo ne ngu shi gang ne ngu shi nva njeli ne ngu yo a zete brra nzhwo rishi ngbe a ebe ana.”<RF q=+><a href="b26.2.8—3:3">Ezi 2:8—3:3</a>
