Nné wehwie ne̱ á bi igbe̱ng she̱ zinye̱, aha ngbe de̱ nze re wie a zhe ne mbe ri shi brro re̱se̱ nka Be̱ne̱ we̱. Á bra bi igbe̱ng bra re-rishi ré ci roshwo, ngbe re bra rwi ebe ngwie̱ ne ga re-nzhwe ge̱zhe̱ kanka kanka ko zohu zhe ne mbe ce̱.<RF q=+><a href="b11.17.1">1Ngg 17:1</a>; <a href="b2.7.17-19">Wru 7:17-19</a>; <a href="b9.4.8">1Sam 4:8</a>
