Ngu a bî ewerento, ne ngu ri ye ringgwe̱ ga re-ngwie̱ zhwozhwo ne ngbo ncwe̱ na ringgwe̱. Ngbe á a kara ewe nna re nzhi nwie Be̱ne̱ ngbe ncwu ringgwe̱ ngu.<RF q=+><a href="b23.66.7">Ish 66:7</a>; <a href="b19.2.9">Rve 2:9</a>
